Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:02.30,cn,,0,0,0,,《永无止境》前情提要\N{\fs14}Previously on Limitless...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.31,0:00:03.81,cn,,0,0,0,,我们每天给他吃一次药\N{\fs14}We give him the pill once a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.82,0:00:05.41,cn,,0,0,0,,这药能提高他的认知能力\N{\fs14}It enhances his cognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:07.66,cn,,0,0,0,,-五粒NZT  -这是做什么\N{\fs14}- Five NZT pills. - What are those for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:08.67,cn,,0,0,0,,随你所愿\N{\fs14}Whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.68,0:00:11.64,cn,,0,0,0,,我还有些额外的NZT  私房货\N{\fs14}I might have a few extra NZT pills, my own stash.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.53,cn,,0,0,0,,我们之后一定会再谈这事\N{\fs14}We are gonna talk about this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:15.22,cn,,0,0,0,,缝合得相当好\N{\fs14}Pretty tidy stitch job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:18.21,cn,,0,0,0,,-是联调局教你的吗  -是的\N{\fs14}- The FBI teach you that? - Yes, it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:19.82,cn,,0,0,0,,瑞秋  我讲真的\N{\fs14}Rach, I really mean it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:21.65,cn,,0,0,0,,真的别告诉任何人这件事  好吗\N{\fs14}when I say don't tell anyone about this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:23.38,cn,,0,0,0,,谁也不说\N{\fs14}Not anyone, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:25.65,cn,,0,0,0,,桑兹杀了丽贝卡的父亲\N{\fs14}Sands killed Rebecca's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.66,0:00:27.30,cn,,0,0,0,,我没能救我父亲\N{\fs14}I couldn't help my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:28.66,cn,,0,0,0,,也许我能救你\N{\fs14}Maybe I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:31.01,cn,,0,0,0,,不要对我说谎  永远不要\N{\fs14}Just don't lie to me. Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:39.00,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}私藏NZT药片  5粒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:38.20,cn,,0,0,0,,"我想在这座不眠之城里醒来"\N{\fs14}"I want to wake up in the city that never sleeps".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:38.20,cn,,0,0,0,,《New York, New York》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:39.80,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}私藏NZT药片  4粒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:40.66,cn,,0,0,0,,法兰克·辛纳屈曾唱过这首歌\N{\fs14}Frank Sinatra once sang that,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:40.72,cn,,0,0,0,,二十世纪流行音乐人物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:42.18,cn,,0,0,0,,现在已是陈词滥调了\N{\fs14}and now it's cliché.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:43.72,cn,,0,0,0,,但是当事情变得糟糕时\N{\fs14}But when things get bad--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:46.45,cn,,0,0,0,,我想说得知桑兹杀了丽贝卡的父亲\N{\fs14}and I would say that living with the knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.91,cn,,0,0,0,,就算很糟糕\N{\fs14}Sands killed Rebecca's father qualifies as bad--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:50.34,cn,,0,0,0,,令我欣慰的是  我能走出门\N{\fs14}it's comforting to know that I can walk out any door,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:53.73,cn,,0,0,0,,不管夜色多深  纽约依旧不眠\N{\fs14}any hour of the night, and New York is still going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.96,0:00:56.74,cn,,0,0,0,,经NZT强化的大脑可有的忙呢\N{\fs14}Plenty to keep an NZT-enhanced mind occupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:00:58.41,cn,,0,0,0,,所以我来到了这里\N{\fs14}That's kind of how I wound up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:01.41,cn,,0,0,0,,胡子\N{\fs14}Beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:02.65,cn,,0,0,0,,胡子  那人有胡子吗\N{\fs14}Beard. The guy had a beard?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:06.18,cn,,0,0,0,,不是  他是说那人脖子上有纹身  联调局的\N{\fs14}No. He's saying the guy had a neck tattoo. FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:08.60,cn,,0,0,0,,素描师有来吗\N{\fs14}Uh, do you have a sketch artist on hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.55,cn,,0,0,0,,有  马蒂\N{\fs14}Yeah. Marty?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:14.85,cn,,0,0,0,,马蒂  介不介意让我来画\N{\fs14}Hey, Marty. Do you mind if I take a stab at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:15.93,cn,,0,0,0,,多谢\N{\fs14}Thanks very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:21.75,cn,,0,0,0,,我知道你想干什么\N{\fs14}I know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:27.55,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱恩·芬奇  你不是这些人想要的英雄\N{\fs14}Brian Finch, not the hero the people want,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:28.81,cn,,0,0,0,,也不是他们需要的人\N{\fs14}or need for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:30.47,cn,,0,0,0,,你到底来这里做什么\N{\fs14}What are you even doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:31.82,cn,,0,0,0,,我要了结这个案子\N{\fs14}I'm about to close this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.83,0:01:33.55,cn,,0,0,0,,我懂  你很擅长查案\N{\fs14}Look, I get it. You're good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:36.62,cn,,0,0,0,,你也许喜欢通过做好事来忘记所有坏事\N{\fs14}And you may like that doing good helps you forget all the bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:38.09,cn,,0,0,0,,但你知道自己其实在做什么吗\N{\fs14}But you know what you're really doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:41.40,cn,,0,0,0,,你在躲避的那些麻烦始终还是会找上门的\N{\fs14}Is ducking a bunch of trouble that's gonna find you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:48.27,cn,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡·哈里斯来电\N忽略
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:50.59,cn,,0,0,0,,你迟早得对她撒谎的\N{\fs14}You're gonna have to lie to her sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:54.04,cn,,0,0,0,,你很擅长素描吧\N{\fs14}You're pretty good at that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.77,0:01:55.62,cn,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:02.05,cn,,0,0,0,,交给你了\N{\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.88,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}警用广播\N发现尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:07.85,cn,,0,0,0,,接到一起可疑犯罪  在大码头公园处\N{\fs14}We got a 10-10, body of a male in his 20s
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:09.02,cn,,0,0,0,,发现一具二十多岁的男性尸体\N{\fs14}found in Grand Ferry Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:10.65,cn,,0,0,0,,各单位请回应\N{\fs14}All units please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:24.66,cn,,0,0,0,,你在吃洋葱圈吗\N{\fs14}Are you eating Funyuns?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:27.57,cn,,0,0,0,,这不是违反规定...\N{\fs14}Doesn't that defy the rules of...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.13,cn,,0,0,0,,今晚不守规矩的不止你一个\N{\fs14}You're not the only rebel tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:31.05,cn,,0,0,0,,一直在回避丽贝卡\N{\fs14}This whole avoiding Rebecca thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:31.96,cn,,0,0,0,,老兄\N{\fs14}Dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:33.55,cn,,0,0,0,,我该怎么做\N{\fs14}What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:37.34,cn,,0,0,0,,我在她身边时  满脑子想的都是\N{\fs14}You know, when I'm around her, all I can think about is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.85,cn,,0,0,0,,我知道是桑兹杀了她爸爸\N{\fs14}how I know that Sands murdered her dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:43.27,cn,,0,0,0,,而这个凶手又正好是保住我小命的人\N{\fs14}That the person who killed him is the same one keeping me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.45,cn,,0,0,0,,-但我能告诉她吗  不能  -不能\N{\fs14}- But can I tell her that? No. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:48.43,cn,,0,0,0,,因为那意味着你得告诉丽贝卡\N{\fs14}Because that would mean you would have to tell Rebecca
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:50.85,cn,,0,0,0,,你是摩拉参议员安插在联调局里的内鬼\N{\fs14}that you are Senator Morra's mole in the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:52.69,cn,,0,0,0,,也就是说你要失去\N{\fs14}Which means losing, let's see,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:55.62,cn,,0,0,0,,酶和免疫力\N{\fs14}the enzyme and your immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:58.51,cn,,0,0,0,,还有我的自由和小命\N{\fs14}And my freedom, my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:00.92,cn,,0,0,0,,而且就算你找到办法避开所有麻烦\N{\fs14}And even if you found some way to dodge all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:04.10,cn,,0,0,0,,你也只能回去做个普通的布莱恩\N{\fs14}you'd have to go back to being just Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.02,cn,,0,0,0,,面对现实吧\N{\fs14}And let's face it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:08.07,cn,,0,0,0,,到时你会想念我的吧\N{\fs14}You'd miss me, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:14.92,cn,,0,0,0,,所以我要告诉你  拒丽贝卡于千里之外\N{\fs14}So I'm telling you, pushing Rebecca away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.28,cn,,0,0,0,,并不是处理办法\N{\fs14}is not the way to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:17.51,cn,,0,0,0,,我没这么做\N{\fs14}That's not what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:21.96,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}丽贝卡·哈里斯来电
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:22.39,cn,,0,0,0,,老兄\N{\fs14}Dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.85,cn,,0,0,0,,你可以忽视她  但你不能忽视我\N{\fs14}You can ignore her, but you can't ignore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:28.09,cn,,0,0,0,,拒接
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.28,cn,,0,0,0,,拒接  接听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.39,cn,,0,0,0,,奇怪了\N{\fs14}Huh. That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.23,cn,,0,0,0,,纽约市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.47,cn,,0,0,0,,-你有所发现吗  -有\N{\fs14}- Did you find something? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.09,cn,,0,0,0,,这把是市政府分发的钥匙\N{\fs14}This is a city government-issued key.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.24,cn,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道\N{\fs14}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:54.82,cn,,0,0,0,,有一次\N{\fs14}One time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:57.38,cn,,0,0,0,,我记住了整个纽约市政府的在线机构名录\N{\fs14}I memorized the whole NYC government directory online.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:59.21,cn,,0,0,0,,这把钥匙以97开头\N{\fs14}And that key starts with a nine-seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:01.29,cn,,0,0,0,,指的是建筑局\N{\fs14}which is the Department of Buildings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.65,cn,,0,0,0,,后面跟着的1  特指的是\N{\fs14}followed by a one, which specifically means
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:06.02,cn,,0,0,0,,曼哈顿许可审批办公室\N{\fs14}the Manhattan Permit Approvals Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:09.92,cn,,0,0,0,,也许你该把调查方向转到那里\N{\fs14}So, maybe you should move your investigation there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.54,cn,,0,0,0,,真是个卓有成效的夜晚\N{\fs14}Let's just say it was a very productive night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:20.37,cn,,0,0,0,,城市的活力暂时让我转移了视线\N{\fs14}While the energy of the city temporarily took my mind off things,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.24,cn,,0,0,0,,但我是对的\N{\fs14}I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:24.58,cn,,0,0,0,,或者另一个布莱恩是对的\N{\fs14}Or the other Brian was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:26.85,cn,,0,0,0,,我知道无法一辈子躲着丽贝卡\N{\fs14}I knew I couldn't avoid Rebecca forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.50,cn,,0,0,0,,我的潜意识不会让我这么做\N{\fs14}My subconscious just wouldn't let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.25,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱恩  你在搞什么\N{\fs14}Brian, what the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:38.25,cn,,0,0,0,,无所谓了\N{\fs14}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:41.38,cn,,0,0,0,,我在纽约警局有熟人\N{\fs14}I know people at the NYPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:42.64,cn,,0,0,0,,你以为他们不会告诉我\N{\fs14}You think that they're not gonna tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:45.19,cn,,0,0,0,,我的顾问在到处亮他的徽章吗\N{\fs14}my consultant is running around flashing his badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:45.97,cn,,0,0,0,,这个嘛\N{\fs14}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.93,cn,,0,0,0,,你为什么一直不接我电话\N{\fs14}Why haven't you been answering my calls?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:49.21,cn,,0,0,0,,我手机没电了\N{\fs14}Well, my phone's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:51.46,cn,,0,0,0,,怪事了\N{\fs14}That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:57.44,cn,,0,0,0,,你下了班还吃NZT吗\N{\fs14}Are you on NZT when you're off-duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:58.98,cn,,0,0,0,,我们说过的\N{\fs14}We've talked about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.91,cn,,0,0,0,,严格来说  我正在工作  丽贝卡\N{\fs14}Well, technically, I am working, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.94,cn,,0,0,0,,只是没在为你工作而已\N{\fs14}I'm just not working for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:05.51,cn,,0,0,0,,-快看那边  -得了吧\N{\fs14}- Look over there. - Nice try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:07.23,cn,,0,0,0,,-不顶用  -不  我说真的\N{\fs14}- Not gonna work. - No, no, I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.41,cn,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fs14}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:48.02,cn,,0,0,0,,应急发电机已启用  请节约用电\N{\fs14}Emergency generators are in use. Please conserve all power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.31,cn,,0,0,0,,麦克  你来为我提神的吗\N{\fs14}Mike, what? You are here to pick me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.26,cn,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs14}Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:53.85,cn,,0,0,0,,-我们在大会议室集合  -马上就来\N{\fs14}- We're assembling in the bullpen. - Be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.20,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}私藏NZT药片  4粒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:59.57,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}私藏NZT药片  5粒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.40,cn,,0,0,0,,你要再吃一粒吗\N{\fs14}You're gonna double your dose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:03.12,cn,,0,0,0,,我希望你不要跟别人说...\N{\fs14}Listen, I really appreciate you not saying anything to... you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:05.22,cn,,0,0,0,,我们会谈这事的\N{\fs14}We are gonna talk about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:09.85,cn,,0,0,0,,有两个独立的地区目前受到停电影响\N{\fs14}We have two distinct areas that are currently affected by the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:13.64,cn,,0,0,0,,金融区在凌晨四点最早受到影响\N{\fs14}The Financial District took the first hit at 0400 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.66,cn,,0,0,0,,有关部门在处理通常会发生的混乱情况\N{\fs14}Authorities are dealing with the usual mess--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.87,cn,,0,0,0,,困在地铁和电梯里的人\N{\fs14}people trapped in subways, elevators,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:19.14,cn,,0,0,0,,以及可能会发生的情况\N{\fs14}as well as the what-ifs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:22.65,cn,,0,0,0,,如果备用电源出故障  医院全黑了怎么办\N{\fs14}You know, what if the backup generator fails and the hospitals go dark
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.42,cn,,0,0,0,,或者信号接收塔坏了  或者水不流了\N{\fs14}or the cell tower goes down or the water stops running?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:27.57,cn,,0,0,0,,因此在东北片区\N{\fs14}So, in the northeast...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:30.27,cn,,0,0,0,,嗨亲们  有电吗  闪电表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:33.27,cn,,0,0,0,,没电  汤米不用上学  真棒...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:35.98,cn,,0,0,0,,我们在新泽西  傻瓜  这儿有电
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.60,cn,,0,0,0,,是啊  但那里还是新泽西  我这儿没电
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.07,cn,,0,0,0,,妈  你和爸那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:42.73,cn,,0,0,0,,这理有店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:46.26,cn,,0,0,0,,妈  我们说过了  要用自动更正
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:49.30,cn,,0,0,0,,对不起  我打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:51.78,cn,,0,0,0,,电也来了  你们要回家来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.08,cn,,0,0,0,,城里会乱作一团的  瑞秋和卡梅伦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.71,cn,,0,0,0,,我让麦克和艾克来接你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:56.35,cn,,0,0,0,,带你们去韦斯切斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.68,cn,,0,0,0,,豆子汤表情\N{\fs14}Pea soup emoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.21,cn,,0,0,0,,她意思肯定是要做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:02.18,cn,,0,0,0,,还是你们要看《驱魔人》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.47,cn,,0,0,0,,瑞秋  卡梅伦  还有两位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.39,cn,,0,0,0,,瑞秋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:04.74,cn,,0,0,0,,瑞秋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:06.92,cn,,0,0,0,,别和联调局的那位陪同乱搞好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:08.92,cn,,0,0,0,,等等  太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.61,cn,,0,0,0,,中指表情  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:13.14,cn,,0,0,0,,叫你们来  是因为得认识到\N{\fs14}You're here because we have to acknowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:16.51,cn,,0,0,0,,我们的金融命脉首先受到停电影响\N{\fs14}that the blackout hit our financial lifeline first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:20.74,cn,,0,0,0,,中国  俄罗斯等国的国力足以发起网络攻击\N{\fs14}Cyber is working on an angle that countries like China and Russia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.01,cn,,0,0,0,,网络处正从这个角度着手调查\N{\fs14}are powerful enough to actually launch a cyber attack
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:24.92,cn,,0,0,0,,他们的网络攻击可以将我们打回中世纪\N{\fs14}that will basically knock us back to the Dark Ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:26.48,cn,,0,0,0,,我不这么看\N{\fs14}Mm, yeah. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.49,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱恩  你有想法吧\N{\fs14}Brian, you have a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:30.39,cn,,0,0,0,,有\N{\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:31.70,cn,,0,0,0,,实际上\N{\fs14}As a matter of fact, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:33.30,cn,,0,0,0,,我们现在还有电\N{\fs14}while we still have power,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:36.43,cn,,0,0,0,,我觉得"犯人"另有其人\N{\fs14}I'd like to propose an alternative offender.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.18,cn,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs14}Come on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:39.09,cn,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.35,cn,,0,0,0,,深红色代表我们市\N{\fs14}So, uh, dark red indicates our city's
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:46.03,cn,,0,0,0,,耗电最多的地区\N{\fs14}highest level of energy consumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:48.46,cn,,0,0,0,,消耗最多的在这里和这里\N{\fs14}The largest consumer being here and here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:50.20,cn,,0,0,0,,尽管这两个地区在地理位置上\N{\fs14}Now, even though these two areas seem
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:51.34,cn,,0,0,0,,看似没什么联系\N{\fs14}geographically disparate,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:54.13,cn,,0,0,0,,它们实际上被风联系了起来\N{\fs14}they are, in fact, connected by the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:59.16,cn,,0,0,0,,停电是顺着全市自然风流推进的\N{\fs14}Now, the power outages are following the natural citywide gust flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.98,cn,,0,0,0,,我环境科学拿的是D-好嘛\N{\fs14}I got a D-minus in environmental science, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:03.88,cn,,0,0,0,,勉强过关  但及格还是及格啊\N{\fs14}It was a real squeaker, but, you know, passing is passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:06.46,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱恩  你父母肯定很骄傲\N{\fs14}Brian, Brian, your parents must have been very proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:09.29,cn,,0,0,0,,没错  好吧  看这个\N{\fs14}They really were. All right, watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.78,cn,,0,0,0,,气流堵在城市里面\N{\fs14}Drafts get stuck inside the city walls,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.78,cn,,0,0,0,,然后突然加速越过高楼大厦\N{\fs14}and then slingshot up and over the high-rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.74,cn,,0,0,0,,你们能看到\N{\fs14}And you can see, it goes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:20.00,cn,,0,0,0,,气流刚好从金融区跑到市中心\N{\fs14}right from the Financial District up to Midtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:22.04,cn,,0,0,0,,你是指断电和天气有关吗\N{\fs14}So you're saying the blackout is weather related?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:23.91,cn,,0,0,0,,我是指根据规律\N{\fs14}Oh, I'm saying that based on the pattern,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.35,cn,,0,0,0,,无论是什么导致断电\N{\fs14}whatever's causing the blackouts
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:28.18,cn,,0,0,0,,都可能被风扩散  但你也知道\N{\fs14}might be getting blown around by the wind, but, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:32.11,cn,,0,0,0,,我得前往本地发电厂确认情况\N{\fs14}I'd have to confirm by visiting local power plants, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.74,cn,,0,0,0,,当然我们仍然应该排除\N{\fs14}And we should still rule out the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:37.16,cn,,0,0,0,,网络战争的可能性\N{\fs14}of cyber warfare, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.19,cn,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:41.66,cn,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.25,cn,,0,0,0,,-好  -佩吉特探员和网络处合作\N{\fs14}- Okay. - Agent Paget will coordinate with Cyber.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:47.18,cn,,0,0,0,,鲍伊探员和专案组的人合作\N{\fs14}Agent Boyle will deal with the task force here on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:48.34,cn,,0,0,0,,我开车送你\N{\fs14}I'll give you a lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:49.33,cn,,0,0,0,,你要去吗\N{\fs14}You're coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:50.60,cn,,0,0,0,,有问题吗\N{\fs14}Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.32,cn,,0,0,0,,不  我只是  不太清楚\N{\fs14}Uh, no, I just... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:53.91,cn,,0,0,0,,这只是个大胆的猜想\N{\fs14}It's kind of a wild guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.17,cn,,0,0,0,,我不想浪费你时间\N{\fs14}I don't want to waste your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.00,cn,,0,0,0,,但你之前都成功了\N{\fs14}Well, I've seen those pan out before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:58.70,cn,,0,0,0,,你可以在路上解释\N{\fs14}You can explain it on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:02.21,cn,,0,0,0,,我们应该告诉麦克和艾克\N{\fs14}We should let Mike and Ike know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:05.01,cn,,0,0,0,,我已经派他们去执行另外的任务\N{\fs14}Oh, I actually kind of sent them on a mission of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:13.61,cn,,0,0,0,,伙计  你到底在干什么\N{\fs14}Man, what in the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:14.82,cn,,0,0,0,,没什么\N{\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.30,cn,,0,0,0,,你在打扮\N{\fs14}You're primping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.46,cn,,0,0,0,,我没在打扮\N{\fs14}I'm not primping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:19.82,cn,,0,0,0,,像孔雀一样\N{\fs14}Like a peacock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.02,cn,,0,0,0,,想打扮帅点\N{\fs14}Got to look good
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:22.76,cn,,0,0,0,,赢得芬奇小妹的芳心吧\N{\fs14}to win over little sister Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:25.11,cn,,0,0,0,,得了吧  已经赢得了\N{\fs14}Oh, please. That ship already came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.33,cn,,0,0,0,,说啊\N{\fs14}Well, do tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:29.74,cn,,0,0,0,,我们一直在发短信\N{\fs14}Yeah, we've been, um... texting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:34.42,cn,,0,0,0,,虽然主要是...我在发\N{\fs14}Which is mainly... you know, me texting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:37.27,cn,,0,0,0,,她没回你短信\N{\fs14}She's not texting you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.21,cn,,0,0,0,,你发了多少短信\N{\fs14}How many texts have you sent?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:43.74,cn,,0,0,0,,表情包算吗\N{\fs14}I mean, do Bitmojis count?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:47.81,cn,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs14}Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.81,cn,,0,0,0,,-你好  -你好  瑞秋  你好\N{\fs14}- Hi. - Hi, Rachel. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:51.87,cn,,0,0,0,,-谢谢你来接我  -不谢\N{\fs14}- Thanks for picking me up. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:59.18,cn,,0,0,0,,要走了吗...\N{\fs14}Are we going or just...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:00.53,cn,,0,0,0,,-系安全带  -走了\N{\fs14}- Buckle up. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.20,cn,,0,0,0,,发电机运转正常\N{\fs14}Generator's operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:07.15,cn,,0,0,0,,我让手下反复检查过了\N{\fs14}I've had my guys check and recheck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:09.57,cn,,0,0,0,,涡轮叶片完全没问题\N{\fs14}Nothing wrong with the turbine blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.24,cn,,0,0,0,,转子运转正常\N{\fs14}The rotor is moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:13.32,cn,,0,0,0,,定子正常\N{\fs14}The stator is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.85,cn,,0,0,0,,完全说不通\N{\fs14}It doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:17.53,cn,,0,0,0,,应该有电啊\N{\fs14}We should be hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:19.08,cn,,0,0,0,,工程师待命\N{\fs14}Engineer, please stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:20.60,cn,,0,0,0,,实压测试\N{\fs14}Actual pressure test.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:22.92,cn,,0,0,0,,你们听到了吗\N{\fs14}You guys hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:30.65,cn,,0,0,0,,莫里斯\N{\fs14}Hey, Maurice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:34.35,cn,,0,0,0,,电力没从发电机里出来\N{\fs14}So the electricity's not making it out of the generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.13,cn,,0,0,0,,没进入输电线\N{\fs14}It's-it's not reaching the power lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:39.20,cn,,0,0,0,,没错  消失得无影无踪了\N{\fs14}Exactly. It's just disappearing into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:41.83,cn,,0,0,0,,你能打开它吗\N{\fs14}Can you open it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:43.40,cn,,0,0,0,,行  退后\N{\fs14}Sure. Step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.95,cn,,0,0,0,,你在找什么\N{\fs14}What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:46.37,cn,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.72,cn,,0,0,0,,如果是经风传播的\N{\fs14}Well, if it was carried by the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:56.95,cn,,0,0,0,,肉眼可能看不到\N{\fs14}it might be something we can't see with the naked eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:11:00.10,cn,,0,0,0,,能借我紫外灯吗\N{\fs14}Do you mind if I borrow that black light?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.31,cn,,0,0,0,,请便\N{\fs14}Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:06.12,cn,,0,0,0,,来  退后\N{\fs14}Here, step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.09,cn,,0,0,0,,那到底是什么\N{\fs14}What the hell is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.26,cn,,0,0,0,,反正是有机体\N{\fs14}Whatever it is, it's organic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:35.67,cn,,0,0,0,,但这能造成断电吗  谢谢\N{\fs14}Could that be causing the blackout though? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:37.19,cn,,0,0,0,,我能跟你谈会儿吗\N{\fs14}Can I talk to you for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:40.98,cn,,0,0,0,,我们得打给纳兹\N{\fs14}We have to call Naz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:43.53,cn,,0,0,0,,这可能是某种生物袭击\N{\fs14}This could be some kind of biological attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:44.58,cn,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.25,cn,,0,0,0,,要知道我昨晚看到了\N{\fs14}You know, I saw this last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:49.85,cn,,0,0,0,,你私自行侠仗义的时候吗\N{\fs14}Out on your Capeless Crusade?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:52.04,cn,,0,0,0,,受害人身上也有这种发光的东西\N{\fs14}This glowy stuff, it was on a murder victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:53.86,cn,,0,0,0,,他手上全是\N{\fs14}It was all over his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:55.88,cn,,0,0,0,,感觉有某种联系\N{\fs14}I mean, it's got to be connected somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:12:00.05,cn,,0,0,0,,所以你违法的行侠仗义之举\N{\fs14}Oh, so your illicit, illegal escapades,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.29,cn,,0,0,0,,也不是毫无收获嘛\N{\fs14}they weren't for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.60,cn,,0,0,0,,我还是做了点好事\N{\fs14}I also do some good, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:03.70,cn,,0,0,0,,这座城市谢谢你\N{\fs14}And the city thanks you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:07.03,cn,,0,0,0,,但这也不能为你的行为开脱\N{\fs14}but... it doesn't make what you did right, or legal,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:07.95,cn,,0,0,0,,我也不会放任你\N{\fs14}or okay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:09.14,cn,,0,0,0,,你想不想跟进这个线索\N{\fs14}You want to follow up on this lead or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.53,cn,,0,0,0,,跟进吧\N{\fs14}Yes, lead on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:14.66,cn,,0,0,0,,我们去了路易斯·瓦格斯的工作地点\N{\fs14}So we headed to the workplace of Luis Vargas,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.62,cn,,0,0,0,,就是手发光的遇害保安\N{\fs14}the dead security guard with the glowing hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:18.38,cn,,0,0,0,,纽约市建筑局\N{\fs14}The New York City Department of Buildings
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:22.73,cn,,0,0,0,,就是管理建筑物的建筑的部门\N{\fs14}is the department that regulates the building of, well, buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.43,cn,,0,0,0,,我在那里碰到了新朋友\N{\fs14}Which is where we ran into my new friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.93,cn,,0,0,0,,赫尔南德斯警探\N{\fs14}Detective Hernandez.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.02,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱恩·芬奇\N{\fs14}Brian Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:29.91,cn,,0,0,0,,白天也打击罪犯啊\N{\fs14}The man fights crime by day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:32.53,cn,,0,0,0,,赫尔南德斯警探  这是丽贝卡·哈里斯探员\N{\fs14}Detective Hernandez, meet Agent Rebecca Harris.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:34.43,cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们同意我们昨晚借用你们的大神\N{\fs14}Thanks for letting us borrow your golden boy last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.28,cn,,0,0,0,,不客气\N{\fs14}Pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.24,cn,,0,0,0,,有什么事\N{\fs14}So what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:37.95,cn,,0,0,0,,我昨晚发现了很奇怪的东西\N{\fs14}Well, last night, I noticed something really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:41.16,cn,,0,0,0,,路易斯·瓦格斯尸体上有橙绿相间的物质\N{\fs14}It was like a green and orange substance on Luis Vargas's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.95,cn,,0,0,0,,我觉得可能与断电有关\N{\fs14}I think it may be connected to the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.54,cn,,0,0,0,,你们有不寻常的发现吗\N{\fs14}Did you guys notice anything unusual here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.63,cn,,0,0,0,,十八层有盏灯坏了\N{\fs14}I mean, there was a broken lamp on the 18th floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:47.89,cn,,0,0,0,,但就目前看来\N{\fs14}but far as we could tell,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.36,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}主档案室\N十八层
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:49.44,cn,,0,0,0,,应该是在黑暗中被打翻了\N{\fs14}it could've been knocked over in the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.90,cn,,0,0,0,,没丢东西\N{\fs14}Nothing's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:53.53,cn,,0,0,0,,那里不是存放着城市建筑的设计图吗\N{\fs14}Isn't that where they store the blueprints for city buildings?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:54.69,cn,,0,0,0,,楼层指南上写着\N{\fs14}Saw it on the directory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:55.90,cn,,0,0,0,,我能看看吗\N{\fs14}You mind if we take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.14,cn,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:12:58.96,cn,,0,0,0,,-电梯没电了吧  -是的\N{\fs14}- Elevators are out, aren't they? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:01.29,cn,,0,0,0,,希望你们体力够\N{\fs14}Hope you packed extra lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:13.29,cn,,0,0,0,,我得加大有氧运动量\N{\fs14}I've got to up my cardio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:15.03,cn,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢  动感单车行吗\N{\fs14}What do you think, spinning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.43,cn,,0,0,0,,你做动感单车吗\N{\fs14}Do you spin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:18.49,cn,,0,0,0,,我可以一整晚追着你跑\N{\fs14}I chase you around all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:26.81,cn,,0,0,0,,平心而论\N{\fs14}Hey, you know, to be fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:28.70,cn,,0,0,0,,如果我昨晚没服NZT出去\N{\fs14}we wouldn't even be following this lead--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:32.17,cn,,0,0,0,,等等  我们本来不会找到这条线索\N{\fs14}hang on-- if I hadn't gone out last night on NZT.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:34.75,cn,,0,0,0,,如果你希望我为了一条\N{\fs14}If you expect me to thank you for a lead
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:37.30,cn,,0,0,0,,让我爬十八层的线索谢谢你...\N{\fs14}that took me up 18 flights of stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:42.12,cn,,0,0,0,,只是你发过誓不会再囤NZT药片了\N{\fs14}It's just, you swore you would stop hoarding NZT pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:43.43,cn,,0,0,0,,我没囤了\N{\fs14}I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.09,cn,,0,0,0,,那是最后一片\N{\fs14}Okay, that was my last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.19,cn,,0,0,0,,还有这一片\N{\fs14}Well, and this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.00,cn,,0,0,0,,麦克给我的\N{\fs14}The one Mike gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:52.01,cn,,0,0,0,,你保证你没对我说谎吗\N{\fs14}You promise you're not lying to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.67,cn,,0,0,0,,我们是六岁小孩吗\N{\fs14}What are we, six years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:56.13,cn,,0,0,0,,我保证  行吗\N{\fs14}I promise, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:57.73,cn,,0,0,0,,没其他药片了\N{\fs14}No more extra pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:57.88,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}私藏NZT药片  5粒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:02.43,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}私藏NZT药片  4粒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.24,cn,,0,0,0,,这里有文件\N{\fs14}Well, files here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:16.65,cn,,0,0,0,,那里有文件\N{\fs14}Files there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:18.66,cn,,0,0,0,,你想分头找吗  这样快点\N{\fs14}You want to split up, cover more ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.48,cn,,0,0,0,,行\N{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:26.06,cn,,0,0,0,,你也许在想我在找什么\N{\fs14}You might be wondering what I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.30,cn,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fs14}So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:29.09,cn,,0,0,0,,但我至少有个想法\N{\fs14}But I at least have a theory:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:31.76,cn,,0,0,0,,有人闯进来找东西\N{\fs14}someone broke in here searching for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:33.37,cn,,0,0,0,,但他们在找什么呢\N{\fs14}But what were they after?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:45.43,cn,,0,0,0,,他们的归档系统简直是文员的噩梦\N{\fs14}I mean, their filing system was a clerical nightmare,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:49.42,cn,,0,0,0,,但我把归错档和放错地方的文件整理好后\N{\fs14}but after I sorted out the documents that were misfiled, or misplaced...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:55.92,cn,,0,0,0,,有个空抽屉很显眼\N{\fs14}...there was one empty drawer that stood out,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:58.27,cn,,0,0,0,,像最近被翻查过\N{\fs14}one that seemed recently raided.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:14:59.82,cn,,0,0,0,,219  东五十三大街
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:04.06,cn,,0,0,0,,海龟湾五十三大街的一栋大楼设计图\N{\fs14}Blueprints for a building on 53rd Street in Turtle Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:07.18,cn,,0,0,0,,那里藏着什么  为了它非得杀死保安呢\N{\fs14}What was there that was worth murdering a guard for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.74,cn,,0,0,0,,这一切和停电又有什么关系\N{\fs14}And how did all this relate to the blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:15.75,cn,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡\N{\fs14}Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:22.04,cn,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡\N{\fs14}Rebecca?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:30.87,cn,,0,0,0,,赫尔南德斯探长  怎么了\N{\fs14}Detective Hernandez, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:32.67,cn,,0,0,0,,先生  请站在原地\N{\fs14}Sir, please hold right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.37,cn,,0,0,0,,-你是布莱恩·芬奇吗  -是\N{\fs14}- Are you Brian Finch? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:36.78,cn,,0,0,0,,阳性\N{\fs14}He's positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.71,cn,,0,0,0,,-你得跟我们走  -什么鬼\N{\fs14}- You need to come with us. - What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.21,cn,,0,0,0,,基于联邦法规第42号法令第70条\N{\fs14}Under 42 CFR 70,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:41.97,cn,,0,0,0,,我们要将你隔离\N{\fs14}we're placing you into quarantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:44.43,cn,,0,0,0,,你接触了可疑物质\N{\fs14}You came into contact with a suspicious substance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:45.54,cn,,0,0,0,,什么  发电厂里的东西吗  到底是什么啊\N{\fs14}What, the stuff from the power plant? What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:46.10,cn,,0,0,0,,尚未确定\N{\fs14}Undetermined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:46.95,cn,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs14}Well, what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.82,cn,,0,0,0,,意思是来源不明\N{\fs14}It means it came from an unknown origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:51.60,cn,,0,0,0,,-你俩都接触了  -好好好\N{\fs14}- You've both been exposed. - Okay, okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:57.55,cn,,0,0,0,,疾病预防控制中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.63,cn,,0,0,0,,还记得你今天说要载我一程吗\N{\fs14}Remember when you offered to give me a ride today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:09.61,cn,,0,0,0,,我本来想拒绝  可你非得坚持\N{\fs14}And I was like, "Nah," And you were like, "I insist."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:11.47,cn,,0,0,0,,我猜你现在后悔了吧\N{\fs14}I'm guessing you regret that decision now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:13.70,cn,,0,0,0,,你说对了\N{\fs14}You're not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:18.05,cn,,0,0,0,,偏偏今天被一起关在一个塑料房子里\N{\fs14}Of all days to get sealed up in a plastic bubble together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:23.94,cn,,0,0,0,,我意思是  你为了昨晚还有药的事生气\N{\fs14}I just mean 'cause you're annoyed about last night and the pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:25.17,cn,,0,0,0,,这事我们已经说清楚了\N{\fs14}We cleared that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:27.27,cn,,0,0,0,,-除非你还是没说实话  -当然不是\N{\fs14}- Unless you're still lying to me. - I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:29.04,cn,,0,0,0,,-那就没事了呗  -那就好\N{\fs14}- Then we're good. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.53,cn,,0,0,0,,我手机没电了\N{\fs14}My phone's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:33.69,cn,,0,0,0,,能借你的用用吗\N{\fs14}Here, can I borrow yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:36.02,cn,,0,0,0,,路易斯·瓦格斯的案子还得调查\N{\fs14}Just got to do some research on the Luis Vargas case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:42.27,cn,,0,0,0,,这有一对"幸运儿"\N{\fs14}Well, here's a lucky pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:45.04,cn,,0,0,0,,我叫斯特金·里德  天体物理学家\N{\fs14}I'm Sturgeon Reid, astrophysicist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:47.47,cn,,0,0,0,,今天我和疾病预防控制中心\N{\fs14}Today, I'm working in tandem with the CDC
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:50.77,cn,,0,0,0,,合作调查你们在发电厂遇到的物质\N{\fs14}to take a look at the substance that you encountered at the power plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:53.54,cn,,0,0,0,,为什么天体物理学家会和疾控中心合作\N{\fs14}Why is an astrophysicist working with the CDC?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:56.22,cn,,0,0,0,,今天我们发现了什么\N{\fs14}What did we discover today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:59.09,cn,,0,0,0,,官方还未确定\N{\fs14}Officials are not yet sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:00.73,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}伊恩·马歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:01.94,cn,,0,0,0,,但"有生源说"大家都听过对吧\N{\fs14}but panspermia, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:01.94,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}认为地球上的生命起源于地外微生物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:03.58,cn,,0,0,0,,地球上的生命来自\N{\fs14}The idea that life on Earth was seeded
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:05.44,cn,,0,0,0,,我们究竟感染了什么\N{\fs14}What exactly were we exposed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:06.25,cn,,0,0,0,,其他星球...\N{\fs14}from other planets, other places...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:07.64,cn,,0,0,0,,麻烦关掉电视好吗\N{\fs14}Would you turn that off, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.66,cn,,0,0,0,,外星生命...\N{\fs14}...extraterrestrial life...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:12.59,cn,,0,0,0,,目前只知道是一种细菌\N{\fs14}We know that it is a bacterium,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:13.96,cn,,0,0,0,,似乎直接\N{\fs14}which appears to be feeding directly
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:17.01,cn,,0,0,0,,以发电厂发的电为食\N{\fs14}off the electricity generated by the power plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.88,cn,,0,0,0,,这并非第一种以电为食的细菌\N{\fs14}It's not the first bacterium to do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:21.18,cn,,0,0,0,,但该物种十分独特\N{\fs14}but this species is unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.21,cn,,0,0,0,,独特\N{\fs14}Unique?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:24.52,cn,,0,0,0,,来自外太空那种独特吗\N{\fs14}As in... from outer space?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:27.43,cn,,0,0,0,,我们在一艘昨天经过象限仪座流星雨下的\N{\fs14}We found traces of the bacterium on a cargo ship
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:30.63,cn,,0,0,0,,货船上发现了该细菌的痕迹\N{\fs14}that passed under the Quadrantids meteor shower yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:34.31,cn,,0,0,0,,所以该物种的起源有可能是...\N{\fs14}So it's possible that the origins of this species could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.34,cn,,0,0,0,,来自外星\N{\fs14}Alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:38.62,cn,,0,0,0,,太赞了\N{\fs14}This is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.42,cn,,0,0,0,,等会儿  我们不会死  对吧\N{\fs14}Wait, we're not gonna die, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.93,cn,,0,0,0,,你们打算怎样阻止细菌传播\N{\fs14}What's the plan to stop the bacteria from spreading?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:44.58,cn,,0,0,0,,因为它以电为食\N{\fs14}Since it's feeding off electricity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:48.03,cn,,0,0,0,,我们希望通过切断曼哈顿的供电让它饿死\N{\fs14}we're hoping to starve it by shutting down all the power in Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.74,cn,,0,0,0,,城市肯定会一团糟\N{\fs14}That's going to be chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.01,cn,,0,0,0,,我们还要在这儿待多久\N{\fs14}And how long do we have to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:54.94,cn,,0,0,0,,因为你们是直接接触者\N{\fs14}Well, since you've had direct exposure,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:57.14,cn,,0,0,0,,所以我建议你们留下来接受观察\N{\fs14}I've recommended you stay in observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:59.48,cn,,0,0,0,,如果你们感到不舒服就按铃叫工作人员\N{\fs14}Alert the attendant if you feel ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:01.36,cn,,0,0,0,,但往好的方面想\N{\fs14}But look on the bright side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:03.18,cn,,0,0,0,,你们有可能创造历史\N{\fs14}You could be making history.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:07.45,cn,,0,0,0,,这一切太蹊跷了\N{\fs14}I don't know about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:08.37,cn,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:09.57,cn,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.64,cn,,0,0,0,,能借下你的手机吗\N{\fs14}Can I borrow your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:13.76,cn,,0,0,0,,要不然就玩猜字游戏\N{\fs14}Or we could play charades.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:16.98,cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.52,cn,,0,0,0,,你爱听哪个电台\N{\fs14}What's your, uh, what's your station?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:25.93,cn,,0,0,0,,都可以\N{\fs14}Anything's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.79,cn,,0,0,0,,我不太听广播\N{\fs14}I don't really listen to the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.86,cn,,0,0,0,,看样子我们能及时离开这里了\N{\fs14}Looks like we're getting out of here just in time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:40.73,cn,,0,0,0,,-我不想走  -快  快\N{\fs14}- I don't want to. - Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.17,cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们\N{\fs14}Hey, thanks for this, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:45.71,cn,,0,0,0,,你也知道有个冷得抓狂的五岁小孩有多烦人\N{\fs14}You can imagine what it's like to have a cold, stir-crazy five-year-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:46.35,cn,,0,0,0,,不  我想要我的...\N{\fs14}No, I want my...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:48.77,cn,,0,0,0,,把包给我  我们得带上包\N{\fs14}Give me the bag. All right, we need the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:49.97,cn,,0,0,0,,包在你那儿吗\N{\fs14}You have the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:55.87,cn,,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:58.86,cn,,0,0,0,,真高兴你们没事...\N{\fs14}Oh, I'm so glad you're... I'm so glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:18:59.90,cn,,0,0,0,,小可爱\N{\fs14}Hi, doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:01.09,cn,,0,0,0,,宝贝儿\N{\fs14}Hi, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:03.54,cn,,0,0,0,,真高兴你们来了  我们很担心\N{\fs14}Oh, we're so glad you got here. We were getting worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:04.46,cn,,0,0,0,,他们是谁\N{\fs14}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:07.43,cn,,0,0,0,,是他们带我们出城的  态度好点\N{\fs14}They got us out of the city. Be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:12.90,cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们照顾我的孩子\N{\fs14}Thanks for taking care of my kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:15.10,cn,,0,0,0,,应该的  先生  这是我们的荣幸\N{\fs14}Of course, sir. It was... it was our pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:19.23,cn,,0,0,0,,我想你们现在该回去了吧\N{\fs14}Well, I assume you'll be going back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:20.47,cn,,0,0,0,,走好\N{\fs14}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:22.11,cn,,0,0,0,,其实我们接到的命令是留下来\N{\fs14}Actually, our orders are to stay
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.90,cn,,0,0,0,,直到事情解决\N{\fs14}until everything's been cleared up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.18,cn,,0,0,0,,谁的命令\N{\fs14}Orders from whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:26.14,cn,,0,0,0,,您儿子  先生\N{\fs14}Your son, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:27.00,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱恩\N{\fs14}Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.93,cn,,0,0,0,,如果会打扰的话  我们可以在外面等\N{\fs14}We can wait outside, if that's easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:32.14,cn,,0,0,0,,没有  当然没有\N{\fs14}Well, no, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.48,cn,,0,0,0,,外面太冷了  快进来\N{\fs14}It's freezing. Uh, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:35.10,cn,,0,0,0,,丹尼斯正在做午餐\N{\fs14}Dennis is just getting lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:36.95,cn,,0,0,0,,我要无谷蛋白的\N{\fs14}I'm gluten-free.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:38.62,cn,,0,0,0,,海龟湾\N{\fs14}Turtle Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:41.00,cn,,0,0,0,,五十三街的第二大道至第三大道段\N{\fs14}The address is on 53rd between 2nd and 3rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.67,cn,,0,0,0,,你知道我们很忙吧\N{\fs14}You do realize we're kind of busy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:46.83,cn,,0,0,0,,我又不是让你给我买彩虹糖  鲍伊\N{\fs14}Yeah, I'm not asking you to go get me some Skittles, Boyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:48.31,cn,,0,0,0,,我确信这很重要\N{\fs14}I know this is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.83,cn,,0,0,0,,丢失的那份设计图\N{\fs14}Look, the missing blueprints
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:51.45,cn,,0,0,0,,是一栋商业大厦的\N{\fs14}were for some kind of commercial building,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.76,cn,,0,0,0,,我在网上查找时发现\N{\fs14}and when I looked online,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:56.07,cn,,0,0,0,,大楼地面以上部分的居住者都很普通\N{\fs14}all of the occupants from the ground up were pretty mundane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:58.68,cn,,0,0,0,,想不通为什么有人把他们作为目标\N{\fs14}I mean, I couldn't figure out why anyone would target them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.33,cn,,0,0,0,,219  东五十三大街
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:00.31,cn,,0,0,0,,但地下室的租户\N{\fs14}But the basement tenant
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:03.74,cn,,0,0,0,,是美国印铸局\N{\fs14}is the United States Bureau of Engraving and Printing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:05.44,cn,,0,0,0,,我知道那地方\N{\fs14}Oh, I know that location.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:07.34,cn,,0,0,0,,银行将污损钞票送到那里\N{\fs14}It's where banks send soiled and defaced bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.65,cn,,0,0,0,,没错  残钞部\N{\fs14}Exactly. The Department of Mutilated Money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:12.90,cn,,0,0,0,,纽约办公室处理整个东北部的残钞\N{\fs14}And the New York office handles the entire northeast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:14.88,cn,,0,0,0,,你能想象那里有多少钞票吗\N{\fs14}I mean, do you know how much cash they must have in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:17.40,cn,,0,0,0,,但不能流通  是等待被销毁的\N{\fs14}Yeah, but it's unusable currency, waiting to be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.69,cn,,0,0,0,,不是所有都会被销毁  很大一部分\N{\fs14}Not all of it. A good fraction of it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.05,cn,,0,0,0,,可以被清洗修复\N{\fs14}can be cleaned and repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:22.18,cn,,0,0,0,,路易斯·瓦格斯  前几天被杀的一名保安\N{\fs14}A security guard, Luis Vargas, was killed the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:25.49,cn,,0,0,0,,很可能就是被偷设计图的人所杀\N{\fs14}presumably by whoever was stealing the blueprints for this address.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:27.02,cn,,0,0,0,,你知道在那名保安身上发现什么了吗\N{\fs14}And do you know what they found on his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.40,cn,,0,0,0,,与造成停电相同的细菌\N{\fs14}The same bacterium that's causing the blackout,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.79,cn,,0,0,0,,只不过路易斯·瓦格斯\N{\fs14}except Luis Vargas was killed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:34.75,cn,,0,0,0,,是在流星雨到达纽约的前一天被害\N{\fs14}a full day before the meteor shower hit New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:37.73,cn,,0,0,0,,你觉得细菌来自别的外星物种入侵\N{\fs14}So you think the bacteria came from some other alien invasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:39.39,cn,,0,0,0,,虽然我不想承认\N{\fs14}As much as I hate to admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.71,cn,,0,0,0,,但我觉得那可能根本不是外星物种\N{\fs14}I think it might not be alien at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:44.76,cn,,0,0,0,,他们说它跟已知细菌相似\N{\fs14}I mean, they say it's similar to known bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:47.68,cn,,0,0,0,,如果是有人培养了新的菌株\N{\fs14}So what if someone cultivated a new strain
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:51.11,cn,,0,0,0,,然后释放并导致停电\N{\fs14}and released it to cause a blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:52.81,cn,,0,0,0,,这可是窃取钞票的完美掩护\N{\fs14}It's the perfect cover to steal a bunch of cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:54.37,cn,,0,0,0,,残钞\N{\fs14}Yeah, mutilated cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:55.55,cn,,0,0,0,,那为什么不抢银行\N{\fs14}Why not hit a bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:57.35,cn,,0,0,0,,因为这更容易\N{\fs14}Because it's an easier target.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.51,cn,,0,0,0,,大部分人认为那些钱基本等同于垃圾\N{\fs14}I mean, people think that money's basically trash,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:00.56,cn,,0,0,0,,也就是说  大部分人根本不会想到\N{\fs14}which means people wouldn't think
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:02.15,cn,,0,0,0,,先去那里查看  但我们想到了\N{\fs14}to look there first, but we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.66,cn,,0,0,0,,如果我们能过去看看\N{\fs14}And if we can just get over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:05.73,cn,,0,0,0,,也许就能阻止盗窃案的发生\N{\fs14}we might be able to stop the heist from happening
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:08.63,cn,,0,0,0,,-并找到造成大范围停电的元凶  -没错\N{\fs14}- and find the people responsible for the whole blackout. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:11.53,cn,,0,0,0,,说是我们  其实只有你\N{\fs14}And by we, I mean you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:14.16,cn,,0,0,0,,因为我们现在仍在这里隔离\N{\fs14}because we're still kind of quarantined here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:15.61,cn,,0,0,0,,好的  我看看我能做些什么\N{\fs14}All right, I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:21.87,cn,,0,0,0,,能把手机还我吗\N{\fs14}Can I have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.18,cn,,0,0,0,,这到底是什么\N{\fs14}What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:25.39,cn,,0,0,0,,-能把手机还我了吗  -不\N{\fs14}- Can I have my phone, please? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:26.40,cn,,0,0,0,,这到底是什么\N{\fs14}What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:27.87,cn,,0,0,0,,这是谁发给你的\N{\fs14}Who-who sent this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:31.62,cn,,0,0,0,,一名探员被派去搜查\N{\fs14}An agent sent to search
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:33.03,cn,,0,0,0,,你所居住的政府房产\N{\fs14}the government property where you're living
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:36.12,cn,,0,0,0,,发现了你藏在黑胶唱片中的疑似NZT药片\N{\fs14}for what looks like NZT pills hidden in your vinyl collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.45,0:21:37.46,cn,,0,0,0,,你跟我说没有多的了\N{\fs14}You told me there weren't any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.47,0:21:39.32,cn,,0,0,0,,派人去搜查我的公寓前\N{\fs14}You know, you could've said something to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:41.40,cn,,0,0,0,,你本可以跟我说一声的\N{\fs14}before sending the cavalry into my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:43.36,cn,,0,0,0,,我确实说了  可你骗了我\N{\fs14}I did say something, and you lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:47.79,cn,,0,0,0,,你到底知不知道随心所欲地使用药物\N{\fs14}Do you have any idea how irresponsible it is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:49.71,cn,,0,0,0,,有多么不负责任\N{\fs14}to use this drug however you want, whenever you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:52.06,cn,,0,0,0,,这些规矩  监管你的药量\N{\fs14}The rules, managing your dosage,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.07,0:21:53.45,cn,,0,0,0,,派人保护你的安全\N{\fs14}keeping a watch out for you--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.46,0:21:55.92,cn,,0,0,0,,都是为了保证你的生命安全\N{\fs14}they're there to keep you alive, to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:58.45,cn,,0,0,0,,得了吧  联调局才不在意我的安全\N{\fs14}Oh, come on! The FBI doesn't care about keeping me safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:21:59.72,cn,,0,0,0,,他们只在意我能发挥作用\N{\fs14}They care about keeping me useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:01.11,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱恩  如果你认为我不在乎\N{\fs14}Brian, if you think that I don't care,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:02.73,cn,,0,0,0,,那你就从未用心\N{\fs14}then you haven't been paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:03.65,cn,,0,0,0,,我带你进的联调局\N{\fs14}I brought you into the FBI,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.66,0:22:04.80,cn,,0,0,0,,-一直支持你  -别说了别说了\N{\fs14}- I've stood up for you - Don't, don't, don't, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.81,0:22:06.11,cn,,0,0,0,,-次数多得数不过来  -你根本不知道\N{\fs14}- more times than I can count. - You have no idea
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:07.89,cn,,0,0,0,,-如果事情无法控制  -你在说什么\N{\fs14}- I know what happens - what you're talking about here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:10.21,cn,,0,0,0,,-我知道会发生什么  -我跟别人不一样\N{\fs14}- if this gets out of hand. - I'm not like anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:13.05,cn,,0,0,0,,没有人跟我的经历一样\N{\fs14}No one else is going through what I am going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:16.10,cn,,0,0,0,,你像个瘾君子一样私藏药片  布莱恩\N{\fs14}You are hiding pills like an addict, Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.11,0:22:18.33,cn,,0,0,0,,我知道你对NZT的副作用免疫\N{\fs14}I know that you are immune to NZT side effects,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.34,0:22:20.91,cn,,0,0,0,,也知道那让你觉得自己与众不同\N{\fs14}and I know that makes you think that you're different somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:22.09,cn,,0,0,0,,但你并不能免疫\N{\fs14}but you are not immune.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:23.19,cn,,0,0,0,,你是在告诉我  我现在怎么想吗\N{\fs14}You're gonna tell me what I think right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:24.42,cn,,0,0,0,,我不是那个意思\N{\fs14}I'm not... That's not what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.43,0:22:25.84,cn,,0,0,0,,不  因为你根本不知道我的想法  丽贝卡\N{\fs14}No, 'cause you don't know inside my head, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:27.41,cn,,0,0,0,,我们没有心有灵犀  知道吗\N{\fs14}We're not psychic twins, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:28.60,cn,,0,0,0,,如果你想听实话\N{\fs14}And if you want the real truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:30.51,cn,,0,0,0,,也许我是对药物上瘾\N{\fs14}I may be addicted to these drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.79,0:22:32.04,cn,,0,0,0,,顺便谢谢你\N{\fs14}Thanks for that, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:33.22,cn,,0,0,0,,但你对我上瘾了\N{\fs14}But you're addicted to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.77,0:22:34.76,cn,,0,0,0,,-解决问题  -什么\N{\fs14}- Solving things, - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.77,0:22:36.15,cn,,0,0,0,,破案  这些让你上瘾\N{\fs14}breaking cases, that's your high.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:38.56,cn,,0,0,0,,而正因有我  你才能做得顺风顺水\N{\fs14}And because of me, you get to do it at a whole new level.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:40.33,cn,,0,0,0,,怎么  你想回到过去的生活吗\N{\fs14}What, you want to go back to your old life?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:41.38,cn,,0,0,0,,处理文书工作\N{\fs14}Keeping up with paperwork
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:43.12,cn,,0,0,0,,事无巨细  谨慎小心\N{\fs14}and crossing your T's and dotting your I's,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:44.43,cn,,0,0,0,,再看着一切以失望告终\N{\fs14}seeing it all end in frustration,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:45.76,cn,,0,0,0,,至少一半时间是这样吧\N{\fs14}what, like, half the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:47.36,cn,,0,0,0,,你跟我一样需要这个\N{\fs14}You need all this as much as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:49.80,cn,,0,0,0,,你跟我一样需要NZT  你心里明白\N{\fs14}You need NZT as much as I do, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.65,0:22:54.90,cn,,0,0,0,,能把手机还给我了吗\N{\fs14}Can I have my phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.60,0:23:01.22,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}私藏NZT药片  4粒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.81,0:23:01.77,cn,,0,0,0,,还有两粒\N{\fs14}Two pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:05.14,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}私藏NZT药片  2粒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:03.48,cn,,0,0,0,,他们只找到两粒\N{\fs14}They only found two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:05.25,cn,,0,0,0,,剩下的呢\N{\fs14}Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.51,0:23:10.67,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸看上去很紧张\N{\fs14}Dad looks stressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:11.84,cn,,0,0,0,,也不能怪他\N{\fs14}Well, can you blame him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:13.50,cn,,0,0,0,,先是停电了\N{\fs14}First there's the power outage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:15.08,cn,,0,0,0,,现在联邦探员又出现在我们家\N{\fs14}Now we have federal agents in the living room,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:16.95,cn,,0,0,0,,进行尴尬的对话\N{\fs14}making awkward conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:20.58,cn,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:22.71,cn,,0,0,0,,也许他只是发现了你跟\N{\fs14}Or maybe he's just picking up on the glances
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.72,0:23:24.63,cn,,0,0,0,,那个长得像加里·格兰特的探员眉来眼去\N{\fs14}between you and the one who looks like Cary Grant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:25.61,cn,,0,0,0,,-妈妈  -好吧\N{\fs14}- Mom. - Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:27.63,cn,,0,0,0,,我就那么一说  瑞秋  别装了\N{\fs14}I'm just saying, Rachel, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:29.78,cn,,0,0,0,,他对你的迷恋全写在他脸上了\N{\fs14}That boy is smitten, it's written all over his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.13,cn,,0,0,0,,拜托别再说了\N{\fs14}Please stop talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.14,0:23:34.17,cn,,0,0,0,,下巴方正  头发茂盛\N{\fs14}Square jaw, still has all his hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:36.48,cn,,0,0,0,,我对天发誓  我会拿这把奶油刀割腕的\N{\fs14}I swear to God, I will cut my wrist with this butter knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.49,0:23:37.95,cn,,0,0,0,,好吧  你有心事\N{\fs14}All right, so something is on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:39.45,cn,,0,0,0,,如果跟他无关  那你在想什么\N{\fs14}If it's not him, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.72,0:23:43.27,cn,,0,0,0,,别跟爸爸说好吗\N{\fs14}Don't tell Dad, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:45.67,cn,,0,0,0,,他会生气的\N{\fs14}He gets so upset about these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.42,0:23:52.55,cn,,0,0,0,,是布莱恩的事\N{\fs14}It's Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.62,0:23:55.39,cn,,0,0,0,,我们那天晚上在他的安全屋里玩\N{\fs14}We were hanging out at his safe house the other night,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:57.94,cn,,0,0,0,,然后他去拿他的唱片\N{\fs14}and he went over to his records,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.57,0:24:00.95,cn,,0,0,0,,似乎从唱片拿出某样东西\N{\fs14}and it looked like he took something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:03.54,cn,,0,0,0,,等他离开以后  我过去找\N{\fs14}So when he left, I went over...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.69,0:24:08.36,cn,,0,0,0,,然后发现\N{\fs14}...and I found...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:15.78,cn,,0,0,0,,我不知道这是什么\N{\fs14}I'm not sure what they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.79,0:24:18.09,cn,,0,0,0,,但我很确定  他变成现在这样\N{\fs14}but I'm pretty sure that they are part of why he is
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:19.66,cn,,0,0,0,,部分原因是这些药\N{\fs14}the way that he is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.76,0:24:22.82,cn,,0,0,0,,但真正让我困扰的是\N{\fs14}But what's really bothering me is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.84,0:24:26.92,cn,,0,0,0,,他因为吃这些药才进入联调局吗\N{\fs14}did he get into the FBI because he's taking these?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.76,0:24:30.14,cn,,0,0,0,,还是这些药是联调局给他的\N{\fs14}Or are they the ones that are giving it to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.23,0:24:32.22,cn,,0,0,0,,我从没看过这种东西\N{\fs14}I've never seen anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.68,0:24:33.73,cn,,0,0,0,,你们还好吗\N{\fs14}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.74,0:24:34.90,cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fs14}Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.91,0:24:37.02,cn,,0,0,0,,好  好  很好\N{\fs14}Yes, yes. Good, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.03,0:24:39.03,cn,,0,0,0,,我帮你摆午餐好吗\N{\fs14}Here, let me help you put out lunch, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.04,0:24:40.87,cn,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fs14}Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.31,0:25:04.72,cn,,0,0,0,,他们洗劫一空\N{\fs14}They cleaned house.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.59,0:25:07.15,cn,,0,0,0,,里面没一分钱了\N{\fs14}Not a dollar inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.39,0:25:09.83,cn,,0,0,0,,只剩不能用的钞票  能用的都拿走了\N{\fs14}Not one you can spend. Cleaned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.04,0:25:11.27,cn,,0,0,0,,看来你的想法是对的\N{\fs14}Looks like you had the right idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.28,0:25:12.67,cn,,0,0,0,,只是我们没有及时赶到\N{\fs14}We just didn't get here in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.68,0:25:15.84,cn,,0,0,0,,所以这是盗窃案  罪犯知道会停电\N{\fs14}So it was a heist, and they did know the blackout was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.85,0:25:18.60,cn,,0,0,0,,我跟残钞部的高级经理谈过了\N{\fs14}Well, I talked to the department's senior manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.61,0:25:20.26,cn,,0,0,0,,他估计保险箱里\N{\fs14}The guy estimates there was
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.27,0:25:22.94,cn,,0,0,0,,原有超过八百万美金\N{\fs14}a little more than $8 million in this safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.28,0:25:27.41,cn,,0,0,0,,鲍伊  我之后再打给你\N{\fs14}Boyle, I have to call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.42,0:25:29.47,cn,,0,0,0,,-看来疾控中心似乎有进展  -好\N{\fs14}- Looks like the CDC might have an update. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.00,0:25:34.12,cn,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡·哈里斯探员  布莱恩·芬奇\N{\fs14}Agent Rebecca Harris, Brian Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.73,0:25:36.78,cn,,0,0,0,,你们不是应该戴面罩之类的吗\N{\fs14}Aren't you guys supposed to be wearing masks or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.79,0:25:39.14,cn,,0,0,0,,细菌被证明无传染性\N{\fs14}The bacterium proved non-communicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.24,0:25:43.56,cn,,0,0,0,,看来它只以非生物来源的电子为食\N{\fs14}Seems it feeds exclusively on electrons found in inanimate sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.57,0:25:45.61,cn,,0,0,0,,意思是我们根本不该被隔离\N{\fs14}Meaning we didn't have to be here in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.47,0:25:47.57,cn,,0,0,0,,你们可以走了\N{\fs14}You're free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.60,0:25:49.31,cn,,0,0,0,,但我们先得测体征\N{\fs14}Well, after we take your vitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.32,0:25:50.30,cn,,0,0,0,,这是法律规定\N{\fs14}Legal issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.31,0:25:52.03,cn,,0,0,0,,证明我们将你们健康送回家\N{\fs14}Proof we sent you home in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.69,0:25:54.39,cn,,0,0,0,,你可以离开了\N{\fs14}You're discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.41,0:25:55.19,cn,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡\N{\fs14}Hey, Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.00,0:26:02.67,cn,,0,0,0,,我们能拿回自己的衣服吧\N{\fs14}We get our clothes back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.23,0:26:04.87,cn,,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\fs14}Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.88,0:26:06.88,cn,,0,0,0,,玛丽  别弄了\N{\fs14}Marie, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.97,0:26:08.09,cn,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fs14}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.82,0:26:10.66,cn,,0,0,0,,坐下  跟我说说话\N{\fs14}Sit down, talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.24,0:26:13.37,cn,,0,0,0,,你在想什么\N{\fs14}What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.02,0:26:16.23,cn,,0,0,0,,你比我更常跟布莱恩谈话\N{\fs14}You talk to Brian more than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.24,0:26:19.73,cn,,0,0,0,,他总是找你解决问题  信任你\N{\fs14}He's always sought you out, trusted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.99,0:26:22.21,cn,,0,0,0,,丹尼斯  我知道你跟他\N{\fs14}Dennis, I know that you have been
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.22,0:26:24.37,cn,,0,0,0,,讨论过这一切\N{\fs14}talking to him about all this, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.38,0:26:27.51,cn,,0,0,0,,我也理解你想隐瞒这些事情\N{\fs14}And I understand if you want to keep it close to the vest,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.52,0:26:30.16,cn,,0,0,0,,只有你确定他没事\N{\fs14}and you wouldn't do that if you didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.17,0:26:31.32,cn,,0,0,0,,你才会这样做\N{\fs14}that he was all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.33,0:26:33.65,cn,,0,0,0,,但布莱恩真的没事吗\N{\fs14}But is Brian all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.97,0:26:34.99,cn,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.74,0:26:37.37,cn,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  他们对他做了什么\N{\fs14}I mean, what are they doing to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.38,0:26:38.56,cn,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\fs14}Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.29,0:26:40.56,cn,,0,0,0,,他很好\N{\fs14}He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.57,0:26:42.36,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱恩不会有事的\N{\fs14}Brian's gonna be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.15,0:26:46.95,cn,,0,0,0,,你知道他们给他药片什么的吗\N{\fs14}Do you know anything about pills or drugs they're giving him?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.77,0:26:50.79,cn,,0,0,0,,你知道什么了\N{\fs14}What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.82,0:26:58.21,cn,,0,0,0,,看来你在认真工作\N{\fs14}Hard at work, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.28,0:26:59.30,cn,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.88,0:27:03.94,cn,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs14}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.72,0:27:05.70,cn,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.41,0:27:09.14,cn,,0,0,0,,我有点不爽疾控中心\N{\fs14}I mean, I'm a little bummed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.15,0:27:11.39,cn,,0,0,0,,烧掉我的快乐分裂乐队的T恤\N{\fs14}that the CDC burned my Joy Division shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.49,0:27:12.75,cn,,0,0,0,,那是原版的\N{\fs14}It was an original.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.91,0:27:16.21,cn,,0,0,0,,你见到丽贝卡了吗\N{\fs14}You seen Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.35,0:27:17.77,cn,,0,0,0,,她跟纳兹在楼上\N{\fs14}She's upstairs with Naz.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.71,0:27:22.19,cn,,0,0,0,,你俩之间在隔离时发生了什么吧\N{\fs14}Something happen between you two, in quarantine?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.20,0:27:24.61,cn,,0,0,0,,说不清楚  做了错事  说了错话\N{\fs14}I don't know, mistakes were made, words were said.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.81,0:27:26.34,cn,,0,0,0,,这应该是我们第一次真正吵架\N{\fs14}I guess it's our first real fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.08,0:27:30.16,cn,,0,0,0,,联络人与顾问的关系本来就够有压力了\N{\fs14}The handler-consultant relationship is stressful enough
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.17,0:27:32.51,cn,,0,0,0,,更何况你们一起被关在塑料房里\N{\fs14}without being thrown into a plastic bubble together.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.52,0:27:33.83,cn,,0,0,0,,你们会没事的\N{\fs14}You guys will get through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.18,0:27:36.59,cn,,0,0,0,,-好吗  -好\N{\fs14}- Okay? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.77,0:27:40.39,cn,,0,0,0,,发电机跟手机信号塔开始断电了\N{\fs14}Generators and cell towers are starting to power down.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.41,0:27:43.02,cn,,0,0,0,,我告诉纳兹我下来看看你有没有发现\N{\fs14}I told Naz I'd come down, check in to see if you had any leads
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.03,0:27:44.35,cn,,0,0,0,,关于残钞抢匪的线索\N{\fs14}on the mutilated money gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.36,0:27:45.77,cn,,0,0,0,,我的确有些线索\N{\fs14}Yeah, I do have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.78,0:27:48.51,cn,,0,0,0,,我认为进行盗窃的人\N{\fs14}So my theory is that whoever pulled off the heist
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.52,0:27:50.16,cn,,0,0,0,,就是传播细菌的人  对吧\N{\fs14}planted the bacteria, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.25,0:27:53.15,cn,,0,0,0,,因为金融区是最先停电的区域\N{\fs14}And since the Financial District was the first to lose power,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.16,0:27:55.53,cn,,0,0,0,,特别是钱伯斯街的两百区\N{\fs14}specifically the 200 block of Chambers Street,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.54,0:27:58.59,cn,,0,0,0,,可以假设那里是细菌最先开始散播的地方\N{\fs14}we can assume that's where the bacteria was first introduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.60,0:27:59.82,cn,,0,0,0,,至于是谁做了这件事\N{\fs14}Now, as for who did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.24,0:28:04.24,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你见过这些科学家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.65,0:28:04.08,cn,,0,0,0,,纽约只有十二个人\N{\fs14}there are only 12 people in the New York area
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.09,0:28:05.79,cn,,0,0,0,,有足够的科学专业知识\N{\fs14}with enough scientific expertise
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.80,0:28:07.71,cn,,0,0,0,,既能设计细菌\N{\fs14}to not only engineer the bacteria,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.72,0:28:10.16,cn,,0,0,0,,又知道如何成功传播\N{\fs14}but also know how to successfully plant it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.17,0:28:12.19,cn,,0,0,0,,如果他们够聪明  能做这些事\N{\fs14}Now, if they were smart enough to do all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.20,0:28:14.39,cn,,0,0,0,,那他们大概也够聪明\N{\fs14}then they're probably smart enough
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.40,0:28:15.87,cn,,0,0,0,,知道躲开监控摄影机\N{\fs14}to stay off security cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.42,0:28:17.62,cn,,0,0,0,,这时就该用上这些了\N{\fs14}And that's where these come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.05,0:28:21.58,cn,,0,0,0,,我尊重你的一些方法  芬奇\N{\fs14}Well, I've come to respect some of your ways, Finch,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.83,0:28:23.04,cn,,0,0,0,,但不代表\N{\fs14}that doesn't mean that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.37,0:28:25.12,cn,,0,0,0,,我愿意挂着广告牌在金融区\N{\fs14}I'm gonna be strolling around the Financial District
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.13,0:28:26.51,cn,,0,0,0,,四处闲晃\N{\fs14}wearing a sandwich board.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.52,0:28:28.68,cn,,0,0,0,,那个区域有很多流浪者\N{\fs14}There's a large homeless population around that area,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.70,0:28:30.74,cn,,0,0,0,,断电时无处可去的人\N{\fs14}people who have nowhere to go during a blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.12,0:28:32.75,cn,,0,0,0,,他们或许能认出罪犯\N{\fs14}They might be able to identify one of the perps.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.76,0:28:34.48,cn,,0,0,0,,或者我打个电话给国安局的朋友\N{\fs14}Or I could just call a friend at the NSA.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.49,0:28:35.74,cn,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fs14}We're not doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.16,0:28:37.05,cn,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.06,0:28:38.60,cn,,0,0,0,,就是  他们应该备份了\N{\fs14}Yeah, they would have a copy
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.61,0:28:40.89,cn,,0,0,0,,这些科学家所有的通话记录\N{\fs14}of every phone conversation these scientists have had.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.90,0:28:42.96,cn,,0,0,0,,是偷偷地去做\N{\fs14}Well, is this on the DL
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.97,0:28:44.51,cn,,0,0,0,,还是得遵照《爱国者法案》\N{\fs14}or are we asserting the Patriot Act?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.36,0:28:47.42,cn,,0,0,0,,你居然支持保护公民隐私\N{\fs14}You're siding to protect people's privacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.43,0:28:48.68,cn,,0,0,0,,真讽刺\N{\fs14}That's ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.92,0:28:50.25,cn,,0,0,0,,不管是不是盗窃案\N{\fs14}Heist or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.26,0:28:51.98,cn,,0,0,0,,有人切断了曼哈顿的电力\N{\fs14}someone shut down the power on Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.99,0:28:53.73,cn,,0,0,0,,这是恐怖主义行为\N{\fs14}That's an act of terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.74,0:28:55.49,cn,,0,0,0,,要不你挂着这个牌子去问\N{\fs14}Or you can wear the sandwich board.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.50,0:28:56.34,cn,,0,0,0,,反正他是你的顾问\N{\fs14}He's your consultant.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.35,0:28:58.33,cn,,0,0,0,,其实我打算多做几个的\N{\fs14}Actually, I was gonna make a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.34,0:28:59.36,cn,,0,0,0,,我们都可以挂起来\N{\fs14}I thought we could all wear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.38,0:29:00.89,cn,,0,0,0,,不用了  你说得对  鲍伊\N{\fs14}No, you're right, Boyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.04,0:29:02.75,cn,,0,0,0,,应该联系国安局\N{\fs14}We should call in the NSA.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.25,0:29:05.10,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱恩  我能和你单独谈谈吗\N{\fs14}Brian, can I talk to you for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.11,0:29:06.07,cn,,0,0,0,,行\N{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.20,0:29:11.38,cn,,0,0,0,,抱歉...\N{\fs14}Look, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.39,0:29:13.08,cn,,0,0,0,,你还记得吗  这一切开始的时候\N{\fs14}You know, when all of this started,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.75,0:29:15.81,cn,,0,0,0,,我们向彼此保证过\N{\fs14}we made promises to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.75,0:29:17.94,cn,,0,0,0,,我说过  无论发生什么事我都会帮你\N{\fs14}I said I would help you through anything
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.95,0:29:19.10,cn,,0,0,0,,只要你不对我说谎\N{\fs14}as long as you didn't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.11,0:29:20.41,cn,,0,0,0,,我知道  我不是故意骗你的\N{\fs14}I know. I didn't mean to lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.42,0:29:21.82,cn,,0,0,0,,我刚刚和纳兹谈过\N{\fs14}I just spoke to Naz.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.12,0:29:24.05,cn,,0,0,0,,她会给你分配一个新联络人\N{\fs14}You're being assigned to a different handler,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.35,0:29:26.31,cn,,0,0,0,,在此之前  你跟着鲍伊\N{\fs14}and in the meantime, you'll work with Boyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.64,0:29:37.18,cn,,0,0,0,,国安局进入刑司委的那一瞬间\N{\fs14}Of course the day the NSA came to the CJC
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.19,0:29:40.20,cn,,0,0,0,,一切都失控了\N{\fs14}was the day everything started spiraling out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.93,0:29:43.76,cn,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  这么多年来国安局一直声称\N{\fs14}You know how for years the NSA's been saying
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.77,0:29:46.06,cn,,0,0,0,,他们只收集电话通讯的元数据\N{\fs14}they only collect metadata from phone conversations?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.07,0:29:47.60,cn,,0,0,0,,真相并非如此\N{\fs14}Well, that's sort of a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.61,0:29:49.25,cn,,0,0,0,,请不要碰\N{\fs14}Don't handle that, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.29,0:29:51.04,cn,,0,0,0,,其实他们记录和存储了\N{\fs14}They're actually recording and storing
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.05,0:29:53.78,cn,,0,0,0,,至少百分之八十美国人的语音通讯\N{\fs14}the audio of at least 80% of Americans' phone calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.79,0:29:54.55,cn,,0,0,0,,在这里签字\N{\fs14}Sign here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.08,0:30:03.22,cn,,0,0,0,,可以碰吗\N{\fs14}Can I touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.62,0:30:12.51,cn,,0,0,0,,成年人每天平均接打五个电话\N{\fs14}The average adult sends and receives about five calls a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.52,0:30:16.05,cn,,0,0,0,,乘以三百六十五天  再乘以十二个嫌疑人\N{\fs14}Multiply that by 365 days, times 12 suspects,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.07,0:30:18.84,cn,,0,0,0,,我要听超过两万一千通电话\N{\fs14}I'm listening to over 21,000 conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.98,0:30:21.04,cn,,0,0,0,,这其中大多与案件毫不相关\N{\fs14}Most of them were totally irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.32,0:30:24.09,cn,,0,0,0,,我早说了别逼走她\N{\fs14}I told you not to push her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.79,0:30:27.79,cn,,0,0,0,,别紧张  你什么也不必说\N{\fs14}Relax, you don't have to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.62,0:30:30.75,cn,,0,0,0,,新的联络人  不是吧\N{\fs14}A new handler? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.06,0:30:33.30,cn,,0,0,0,,你觉得这样你就能搞定了吗\N{\fs14}You think you're gonna be able to make that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.52,0:30:37.25,cn,,0,0,0,,这里还有谁会像她那样保护你\N{\fs14}Is there anyone else here who will protect you like she did?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.61,0:30:39.60,cn,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么解决\N{\fs14}How are you going to fix this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.61,0:30:40.75,cn,,0,0,0,,我解决不了\N{\fs14}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.63,0:30:45.92,cn,,0,0,0,,能不能...\N{\fs14}Ma... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.45,0:30:48.73,cn,,0,0,0,,刚才那通我没听清  能不能...\N{\fs14}I can't... I can't make out this last track. If you...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.74,0:30:50.27,cn,,0,0,0,,对  回放一下  谢谢\N{\fs14}Yeah, rewind that. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.00,0:30:53.86,cn,,0,0,0,,说到哪儿了  对了\N{\fs14}Where was I? Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.87,0:30:56.42,cn,,0,0,0,,范围缩小到伊恩·马歇尔和斯特金·里德\N{\fs14}It's down to Ian Marshall and Sturgeon Reid.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.64,0:30:59.82,cn,,0,0,0,,我并不反对你的观点  只是我们识别不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.96,0:31:02.35,cn,,0,0,0,,即使真有外星人在给我们制造麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.55,0:31:04.12,cn,,0,0,0,,人类还没有准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.13,0:31:05.76,cn,,0,0,0,,或许在我们孙辈那一代能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.77,0:31:07.28,cn,,0,0,0,,但我们有生之年做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.40,0:31:08.43,cn,,0,0,0,,敢不敢打个赌
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.44,0:31:10.57,cn,,0,0,0,,我赌一美元能在有生之年\N{\fs14}One dollar says we will find evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.58,0:31:12.11,cn,,0,0,0,,发现外星生物存在的证据\N{\fs14}of alien life in our lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.12,0:31:13.97,cn,,0,0,0,,我赌一美元发现不了\N{\fs14}And one dollar says we won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.34,0:31:21.05,cn,,0,0,0,,我觉得你欠马歇尔博士一美元  里德博士\N{\fs14}I believe you owe Dr. Marshall a dollar, Dr. Reid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.79,0:31:22.77,cn,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事\N{\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.43,0:31:24.70,cn,,0,0,0,,我们这是在干什么\N{\fs14}What are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.71,0:31:27.04,cn,,0,0,0,,你们两个进行了一场朋友间的较量\N{\fs14}You two have kind of a friendly rivalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.21,0:31:28.20,cn,,0,0,0,,算是吧\N{\fs14}Ish.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.50,0:31:30.56,cn,,0,0,0,,两位著名的天体物理学家\N{\fs14}Just a couple of eminent astrophysicists
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.57,0:31:32.35,cn,,0,0,0,,争论我们能否在将来几十年内\N{\fs14}debating whether or not we discover evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.36,0:31:34.65,cn,,0,0,0,,发现外星生物的踪迹\N{\fs14}of extraterrestrial life within the next couple of decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.66,0:31:36.56,cn,,0,0,0,,你们甚至还为此打了个赌  是吧\N{\fs14}You even made a bet about it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.64,0:31:38.08,cn,,0,0,0,,赌注一美元\N{\fs14}For one dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.77,0:31:40.29,cn,,0,0,0,,你怎么会知道这事\N{\fs14}How could you possibly know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.30,0:31:44.48,cn,,0,0,0,,一边是多疑的斯特金·里德\N{\fs14}On the one hand, we have the skeptic Sturgeon Reid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.83,0:31:47.54,cn,,0,0,0,,一边是把金钱和自尊押在外星人身上的\N{\fs14}Laying his money and pride on the ETs,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.03,0:31:49.42,cn,,0,0,0,,伊恩·马歇尔博士\N{\fs14}Dr. Ian Marshall.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.23,0:31:52.45,cn,,0,0,0,,你决心要赢这一美元  是吧\N{\fs14}And you saw to it you were gonna win that buck, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.81,0:31:55.98,cn,,0,0,0,,我并没有承认\N{\fs14}Uh, I'm not conceding that
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.99,0:31:57.68,cn,,0,0,0,,有过这样的赌约\N{\fs14}such a bet even happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.75,0:31:59.87,cn,,0,0,0,,不需要你承认\N{\fs14}We don't need you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.88,0:32:01.36,cn,,0,0,0,,我们向沃尔科特大学的教务长\N{\fs14}Uh, we shared our concerns
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.37,0:32:03.39,cn,,0,0,0,,表达了我们的疑虑\N{\fs14}with the provost of Walcott University,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.40,0:32:06.30,cn,,0,0,0,,她允许我们进你的实验室看一看\N{\fs14}and she agreed to let us take a look in your lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.31,0:32:09.12,cn,,0,0,0,,我们发现了微量导致断电的细菌\N{\fs14}We found trace amounts of the bacteria causing the outages,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.13,0:32:10.87,cn,,0,0,0,,和一些毁掉的培养菌\N{\fs14}some destroyed cultures.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.37,0:32:12.54,cn,,0,0,0,,有什么解释吗\N{\fs14}Care to explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.79,0:32:13.96,cn,,0,0,0,,我来帮你起个头\N{\fs14}I'll get you started.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.97,0:32:16.79,cn,,0,0,0,,你发现了一种专门以电子为食的细菌\N{\fs14}You discovered a species of bacteria that feeds on electrons,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.80,0:32:18.29,cn,,0,0,0,,但是你没有公开\N{\fs14}but you kept it to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.61,0:32:20.73,cn,,0,0,0,,你在金融区释放了菌落\N{\fs14}You released a colony in the Financial District
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.74,0:32:23.25,cn,,0,0,0,,而且是趁流星雨到来之际释放\N{\fs14}and timed that release with the passage of the meteor shower,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.27,0:32:25.33,cn,,0,0,0,,这样人们就会联想到外星人\N{\fs14}so people would start thinking aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.34,0:32:27.77,cn,,0,0,0,,这计划挺聪明的  兄弟  别谦虚\N{\fs14}It's a clever plan, dude, own it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.03,0:32:31.21,cn,,0,0,0,,而且我们逮了你个正着  所以...\N{\fs14}Plus we already got you kind of dead to rights, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.23,0:32:33.46,cn,,0,0,0,,其实  是我手下一位助理研究员\N{\fs14}Actually, it was one of my research assistants
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.47,0:32:35.22,cn,,0,0,0,,发现了这种细菌\N{\fs14}who discovered the bacteria,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.23,0:32:39.37,cn,,0,0,0,,但我说服她不要公布这一发现\N{\fs14}but I convinced her not to report it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.80,0:32:41.44,cn,,0,0,0,,我只是想赢\N{\fs14}I-I just wanted to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.55,0:32:44.53,cn,,0,0,0,,在某一瞬间  你不再满足于此\N{\fs14}And at some point you started to want more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.83,0:32:45.89,cn,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fs14}I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.09,0:32:47.79,cn,,0,0,0,,从残钞部\N{\fs14}The theft of $8 million
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.80,0:32:50.01,cn,,0,0,0,,盗取八百万美元\N{\fs14}from the Department of Mutilated Money.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.47,0:32:55.20,cn,,0,0,0,,路易斯·瓦格斯  两天前被你杀害的那个保安\N{\fs14}Luis Vargas, the security guard you murdered two nights ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.62,0:32:57.05,cn,,0,0,0,,你引发了断电\N{\fs14}You caused the blackout,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.06,0:32:59.76,cn,,0,0,0,,又以此为掩护大发横财\N{\fs14}then used it as cover to make yourself rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.11,0:33:01.96,cn,,0,0,0,,你在偷设计图的时候被他发现了\N{\fs14}He surprised you when you were stealing the plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.97,0:33:02.65,cn,,0,0,0,,不  不  不\N{\fs14}No, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.66,0:33:03.96,cn,,0,0,0,,我没有杀人\N{\fs14}I am not a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.98,0:33:05.77,cn,,0,0,0,,我不是小偷\N{\fs14}I-I'm not a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.94,0:33:07.18,cn,,0,0,0,,我是终身教授\N{\fs14}I have tenure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.49,0:33:08.68,cn,,0,0,0,,两晚前吗\N{\fs14}Two nights ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.63,0:33:11.65,cn,,0,0,0,,这起谋杀案什么时候发生的\N{\fs14}What time did this murder happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.67,0:33:15.14,cn,,0,0,0,,死亡时间估计是在九点到十一点\N{\fs14}Time of death is estimated between 9:00 and 11:00 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.75,0:33:17.89,cn,,0,0,0,,别慌  伊恩\N{\fs14}Relax, Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.46,0:33:20.80,cn,,0,0,0,,周二晚上我和马歇尔博士在哥伦比亚大学\N{\fs14}Tuesday night, Dr. Marshall and I gave a lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.81,0:33:22.42,cn,,0,0,0,,开了场联合讲座\N{\fs14}together at Columbia.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.43,0:33:26.22,cn,,0,0,0,,一千四百名学生可以替我们作证\N{\fs14}1,400 students will attest for our whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.61,0:33:29.51,cn,,0,0,0,,马歇尔博士也许释放了细菌\N{\fs14}Uh, he may have planted the bacteria...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.08,0:33:33.21,cn,,0,0,0,,但他绝对没谋杀任何人\N{\fs14}but Dr. Marshall didn't kill anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.76,0:33:48.13,cn,,0,0,0,,请避开豪特大道与格兰大道以及\N{\fs14}Please avoid all streets between Hoten and Grand,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.14,0:33:49.84,cn,,0,0,0,,艾伦大道与东河之间所有街道\N{\fs14}Allen and the East River.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.85,0:33:52.37,cn,,0,0,0,,政府官员已重新开通威廉斯堡大桥\N{\fs14}City officials has reopened the Williamsburg Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.38,0:33:54.56,cn,,0,0,0,,-也重建了检查站  -拜托\N{\fs14}- and a checkpoint has been reestablished, - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.72,0:33:56.77,cn,,0,0,0,,-因此造成严重交通堵塞  -拜托\N{\fs14}- causing major traffic delays. - Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.56,0:33:59.45,cn,,0,0,0,,两位好\N{\fs14}Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.46,0:34:00.48,cn,,0,0,0,,你们还好吗\N{\fs14}How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.79,0:34:02.68,cn,,0,0,0,,这问题真蠢  当然不好\N{\fs14}Oh, that's a dumb question. It's not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.80,0:34:05.46,cn,,0,0,0,,因为路被堵住了  对吧\N{\fs14}That's the thing about standstill traffic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.47,0:34:06.57,cn,,0,0,0,,真是难受啊\N{\fs14}It's the pits.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.71,0:34:07.98,cn,,0,0,0,,你是寇依·马丁逊\N{\fs14}Corey Martinson?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.16,0:34:10.18,cn,,0,0,0,,你就是伊恩·马歇尔的研究助理吧\N{\fs14}You're Ian Marshall's research assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.66,0:34:12.10,cn,,0,0,0,,当你默认了\N{\fs14}I'll take that as a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.11,0:34:13.31,cn,,0,0,0,,我们是联调局的人\N{\fs14}So we're from the FBI
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.32,0:34:14.74,cn,,0,0,0,,我们得知你的老板是此次\N{\fs14}and we just learned that your boss is the one
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.75,0:34:16.79,cn,,0,0,0,,城市瘫痪的始作俑者\N{\fs14}behind the hoax that paralyzed the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.02,0:34:18.32,cn,,0,0,0,,据他所说\N{\fs14}And the way he tells it,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.35,0:34:20.56,cn,,0,0,0,,你帮他培育出了细菌\N{\fs14}you helped him fabricate the bacteria that did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.57,0:34:22.78,cn,,0,0,0,,他还说  你是他唯一的搭档\N{\fs14}Also, he said you were his only partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.80,0:34:24.03,cn,,0,0,0,,请问你是否愿意作出\N{\fs14}Would you be willing to testify
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.05,0:34:26.39,cn,,0,0,0,,对你老板不利的证明呢\N{\fs14}against your boss in the charges he faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.45,0:34:29.51,cn,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs14}Um... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.80,0:34:31.58,cn,,0,0,0,,慢着  你们怎么知道我在这儿\N{\fs14}Wait, how did you find me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.59,0:34:33.14,cn,,0,0,0,,这里  我们只是在等你露面\N{\fs14}Here? Oh, we just waited for you to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.15,0:34:33.97,cn,,0,0,0,,你懂吧  毕竟\N{\fs14}I mean, this is, after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.98,0:34:35.72,cn,,0,0,0,,这是现在出城的唯一道路\N{\fs14}the only way out of the city at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.73,0:34:37.65,cn,,0,0,0,,当然  联调局做了点手脚\N{\fs14}We at the FBI kind of set it up that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.66,0:34:38.57,cn,,0,0,0,,重点是\N{\fs14}Thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.58,0:34:41.00,cn,,0,0,0,,有人想趁着此次城市断电事件\N{\fs14}somebody used the blackout to stage a robbery
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.01,0:34:42.46,cn,,0,0,0,,盗窃残钞部的财产\N{\fs14}of the Department of Mutilated Money.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.47,0:34:45.49,cn,,0,0,0,,比如某个  怎么说呢  薪水过低\N{\fs14}Someone, like, say, an underpaid research assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.51,0:34:47.20,cn,,0,0,0,,学生债务缠身的研究助理\N{\fs14}with crushing amounts of student debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.21,0:34:50.35,cn,,0,0,0,,此人将老板的小小恶作剧当作自己的机会\N{\fs14}Someone who saw her boss' relatively harmless hoax as an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.36,0:34:52.30,cn,,0,0,0,,这个人的表亲\N{\fs14}That same somebody had a cousin
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.31,0:34:53.56,cn,,0,0,0,,还因持械抢劫坐过牢\N{\fs14}who did time for armed robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.58,0:34:54.17,cn,,0,0,0,,你好  弗兰克\N{\fs14}Hi, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.18,0:34:55.46,cn,,0,0,0,,他们合伙想出了一个办法\N{\fs14}Together, they came up with a plan
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.47,0:34:56.95,cn,,0,0,0,,于是从亚马逊网站上订购了\N{\fs14}and they even ordered a ridiculous amount
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.96,0:34:59.40,cn,,0,0,0,,一大堆洗衣粉以及化学溶剂\N{\fs14}of laundry detergents and solvents from Amazon
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.41,0:35:00.44,cn,,0,0,0,,用来清洁他们偷的钱\N{\fs14}to clean the money they stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.45,0:35:01.97,cn,,0,0,0,,这话听着熟悉吗\N{\fs14}Any of this sounding familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.07,0:35:03.07,cn,,0,0,0,,想否认吧\N{\fs14}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.08,0:35:05.52,cn,,0,0,0,,你们俩不介意我们打开救护车的后门看一看吧\N{\fs14}Now, would you two mind if we took a look in the back of this ambulance,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.54,0:35:07.47,cn,,0,0,0,,不用说  车是从私人紧急医疗服务租的\N{\fs14}no doubt rented from a private EMS service
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.48,0:35:09.04,cn,,0,0,0,,以便隔离期间可以自由行动\N{\fs14}to move about freely in the quarantine?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.55,0:35:20.56,cn,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.57,0:35:21.97,cn,,0,0,0,,我们没拿到逮捕令\N{\fs14}We weren't able to get a warrant,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.98,0:35:23.45,cn,,0,0,0,,因为停电了\N{\fs14}with all the power being out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.49,0:35:25.96,cn,,0,0,0,,但你试图逃跑倒是给了我合理理由\N{\fs14}But that attempted escape is probable cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.91,0:35:29.44,cn,,0,0,0,,而朋友  那些就是铁证\N{\fs14}And that, my friend, is irrefutable evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.98,0:35:31.76,cn,,0,0,0,,想要美好时光\N{\fs14}请拨打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.25,0:35:35.54,cn,,0,0,0,,上面写的什么\N{\fs14}What's it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.61,0:35:41.28,cn,,0,0,0,,你说有没有人试图拨这个电话\N{\fs14}I wonder if anyone's ever tried calling this number.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.29,0:35:43.65,cn,,0,0,0,,憧憬着电话另一边就是美好时光\N{\fs14}Think there's actually a good time at the end of this line?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.89,0:35:44.89,cn,,0,0,0,,你说呢  打打看\N{\fs14}Huh? Should we call?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.08,0:35:46.55,cn,,0,0,0,,你想的话可以打打看\N{\fs14}You can give it a shot if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.30,0:35:48.95,cn,,0,0,0,,我要回家了  兄弟\N{\fs14}I'm gonna go home, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.23,0:35:53.28,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱恩\N{\fs14}Hey, Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.82,0:35:56.24,cn,,0,0,0,,我本来不想说的...\N{\fs14}Pains me to say it, but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.47,0:35:58.16,cn,,0,0,0,,这样也不算最糟  是吧\N{\fs14}it's not the worst thing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.84,0:36:00.21,cn,,0,0,0,,我俩一起工作\N{\fs14}Us working together?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.56,0:36:02.97,cn,,0,0,0,,其实我并不是真想回家\N{\fs14}I didn't really want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.98,0:36:05.27,cn,,0,0,0,,但我绝对不想回刑司委\N{\fs14}I sure as hell didn't want to go back to the CJC.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.37,0:36:07.34,cn,,0,0,0,,我只想到一个可以去的地方\N{\fs14}There's only one place I could think to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.35,0:36:09.41,cn,,0,0,0,,一个还有人爱我的地方\N{\fs14}the one place people still love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.42,0:36:10.89,cn,,0,0,0,,因为他们没有其他选择\N{\fs14}Because they have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.28,0:36:13.74,cn,,0,0,0,,卡梅隆\N{\fs14}Hey, Cameron.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.75,0:36:14.56,cn,,0,0,0,,你这就要走吗\N{\fs14}You leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.57,0:36:15.84,cn,,0,0,0,,我还想着和你们吃完饭呢\N{\fs14}I was hoping to catch you guys for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.85,0:36:18.15,cn,,0,0,0,,是啊  听说电力很快就会恢复\N{\fs14}Yeah, we heard it shouldn't be long before the power's restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.16,0:36:20.48,cn,,0,0,0,,如果我是你  我会马上离开\N{\fs14}Hey, if I were you, I'd turn around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.70,0:36:21.43,cn,,0,0,0,,什么  为什么\N{\fs14}What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.44,0:36:22.61,cn,,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道发生了什么\N{\fs14}I don't know what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.62,0:36:23.69,cn,,0,0,0,,但我绝对听到他们提到了你\N{\fs14}but I definitely heard your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.70,0:36:26.34,cn,,0,0,0,,能跑则跑吧\N{\fs14}So run while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.85,0:36:34.90,cn,,0,0,0,,你们好啊\N{\fs14}Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.29,0:36:36.26,cn,,0,0,0,,发生了什么\N{\fs14}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.86,0:36:37.84,cn,,0,0,0,,坐下  布莱恩\N{\fs14}Sit down, Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.33,0:36:41.42,cn,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.18,0:36:44.03,cn,,0,0,0,,有种不详的预感\N{\fs14}That sounds ominous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.63,0:36:49.59,cn,,0,0,0,,妈\N{\fs14}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.80,0:36:50.70,cn,,0,0,0,,你还好吧\N{\fs14}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.13,0:36:53.18,cn,,0,0,0,,要知道  布莱恩...\N{\fs14}You know, Brian...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.58,0:36:57.92,cn,,0,0,0,,我一直相信你有过人之处\N{\fs14}I always knew that you had something special about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.70,0:36:59.79,cn,,0,0,0,,心地善良\N{\fs14}A good heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.43,0:37:02.92,cn,,0,0,0,,体贴  关心他人\N{\fs14}You were sensitive, you cared about other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.23,0:37:04.48,cn,,0,0,0,,就算你一时冲动\N{\fs14}Even if you were being impulsive,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.49,0:37:06.19,cn,,0,0,0,,就算你做的事情\N{\fs14}even if the things you were doing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.20,0:37:08.53,cn,,0,0,0,,看上去很自私\N{\fs14}looked selfish on the face of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.63,0:37:15.82,cn,,0,0,0,,正因为我深信你身上的闪光点\N{\fs14}I believed in that light that was in you so much that, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.15,0:37:17.68,cn,,0,0,0,,导致我忽略了很多事\N{\fs14}I let a lot of things slip by.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.52,0:37:19.86,cn,,0,0,0,,当我如往常一样\N{\fs14}Finding pot in your jeans
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.87,0:37:21.69,cn,,0,0,0,,洗你留下的裤子时发现了大麻\N{\fs14}when you left them out for me to wash as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.70,0:37:22.42,cn,,0,0,0,,妈  听我说...\N{\fs14}Mom, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.43,0:37:23.62,cn,,0,0,0,,不  让我说完\N{\fs14}No. Let me finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.22,0:37:27.77,cn,,0,0,0,,我想我们也许能\N{\fs14}I figured that we would find
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.78,0:37:29.76,cn,,0,0,0,,找到某种平衡点  你懂吗\N{\fs14}some kind of balance, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.43,0:37:32.80,cn,,0,0,0,,你爸会约束你  限制你\N{\fs14}Your father would give you discipline, some structure;
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.81,0:37:34.62,cn,,0,0,0,,我会给你空间去折腾\N{\fs14}I would give you room to run
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.63,0:37:36.09,cn,,0,0,0,,这样你就能自己想通\N{\fs14}so you could figure things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.14,0:37:37.59,cn,,0,0,0,,而且我真的觉得\N{\fs14}And I honestly thought
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.60,0:37:39.49,cn,,0,0,0,,那正是你现在的状态\N{\fs14}that's what was happening to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.79,0:37:43.95,cn,,0,0,0,,我原以为  也许他终于想明白了\N{\fs14}I thought, maybe he's finally figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.41,0:37:48.72,cn,,0,0,0,,我真是个傻瓜\N{\fs14}Ugh. What an idiot I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.03,0:37:50.36,cn,,0,0,0,,别这么说  妈  你...\N{\fs14}Come on, Mom, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.37,0:37:50.47,cn,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.59,0:37:52.96,cn,,0,0,0,,-这些到底是什么  -天啊\N{\fs14}- What the hell are these? - Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.04,0:37:55.61,cn,,0,0,0,,你想告诉我它们是什么吗\N{\fs14}You want to tell me about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.63,0:37:57.28,cn,,0,0,0,,因为你爸不肯说\N{\fs14}Because your father won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.88,0:37:59.21,cn,,0,0,0,,我们结婚四十二年了\N{\fs14}We've been married for 42 years
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.22,0:38:00.69,cn,,0,0,0,,没有什么事\N{\fs14}and there has never been a single thing
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.70,0:38:01.94,cn,,0,0,0,,是我们不能谈论的\N{\fs14}that we could not discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.95,0:38:05.56,cn,,0,0,0,,所以不管这些是什么  问题一定很严重\N{\fs14}So whatever these are must be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.63,0:38:07.39,cn,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\fs14}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.40,0:38:09.34,cn,,0,0,0,,别叫我  这是你和你妈之间的事\N{\fs14}Oh, no. This is between you and your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.37,0:38:12.17,cn,,0,0,0,,你把这些东西带回咱们家\N{\fs14}You brought this into our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.22,0:38:13.59,cn,,0,0,0,,不  我没有  我没有\N{\fs14}No, I didn't. No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.60,0:38:15.81,cn,,0,0,0,,从你把妹妹卷进去的那一刻起\N{\fs14}The moment you got your sister into this,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.11,0:38:17.27,cn,,0,0,0,,你就做错了\N{\fs14}you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.60,0:38:19.11,cn,,0,0,0,,到处乱放这些药片\N{\fs14}Leaving these pills lying around,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.12,0:38:21.18,cn,,0,0,0,,让她去你那间\N{\fs14}having her come to that safe house
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.23,0:38:23.13,cn,,0,0,0,,被神秘赠与的安全屋\N{\fs14}that you have been mysteriously given.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.15,0:38:24.92,cn,,0,0,0,,你把你妹妹置于危险中\N{\fs14}You put your sister in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.93,0:38:25.75,cn,,0,0,0,,不  我没有\N{\fs14}No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.76,0:38:27.61,cn,,0,0,0,,卧底去了你那里\N{\fs14}Undercover agents coming over,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.62,0:38:29.64,cn,,0,0,0,,在餐桌上失血致死\N{\fs14}bleeding out on the kitchen table.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.03,0:38:32.15,cn,,0,0,0,,瑞秋\N{\fs14}Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.16,0:38:33.21,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱恩  住嘴\N{\fs14}Brian, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.23,0:38:35.76,cn,,0,0,0,,我不会再睁一只眼闭一只眼了\N{\fs14}I am not turning a blind eye anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.77,0:38:37.58,cn,,0,0,0,,我不知道这些药片是什么\N{\fs14}I don't know what these pills are.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.59,0:38:38.62,cn,,0,0,0,,我也不想知道\N{\fs14}I don't want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.37,0:38:41.90,cn,,0,0,0,,我们一家已经卷进来了\N{\fs14}And I don't want our family any deeper in this
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.91,0:38:42.98,cn,,0,0,0,,我不想我们陷得更深\N{\fs14}than we already are.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.97,0:38:49.42,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}私藏NZT药片  2粒
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.43,0:38:50.29,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}私藏NZT药片  0粒
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.27,0:38:54.44,cn,,0,0,0,,妈\N{\fs14}Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.93,0:38:56.70,cn,,0,0,0,,我不能把一切都告诉你  但我可以解释\N{\fs14}I can't tell you everything, but I can explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.71,0:38:59.73,cn,,0,0,0,,布莱恩  别说了  我不需要任何借口\N{\fs14}Brian, no. I don't want any more excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.74,0:39:02.15,cn,,0,0,0,,因为除非你开始做出不同的选择\N{\fs14}Because unless you start making some different choices,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.16,0:39:04.06,cn,,0,0,0,,否则这里不欢迎你\N{\fs14}you are not welcome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.86,0:39:08.56,cn,,0,0,0,,我爱你  布莱恩  可是...\N{\fs14}I love you, Brian, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.04,0:39:10.13,cn,,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fs14}just...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.13,0:39:12.26,cn,,0,0,0,,这样不行\N{\fs14}no.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.41,0:39:24.00,cn,,0,0,0,,*纸杯之船*\N{\fs14}*Paper cup of the boat*
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.98,0:39:29.14,cn,,0,0,0,,*起伏的海浪*\N{\fs14}*Heaving chest of the sea*
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.22,0:39:33.77,cn,,0,0,0,,*载着我们俩*\N{\fs14}*Carry both of us*
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.24,0:39:38.04,cn,,0,0,0,,*载着她  也载着我*\N{\fs14}*Carry her, carry me*
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.67,0:39:45.06,cn,,0,0,0,,*从我们出生的地方*\N{\fs14}*From the place we were born*
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.33,0:39:49.92,cn,,0,0,0,,*去向自由之地*\N{\fs14}*To the land of the free*
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.80,0:39:54.26,cn,,0,0,0,,*载着我们俩*\N{\fs14}*Carry both of us*
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.38,0:39:58.18,cn,,0,0,0,,*载着她  也载着我*\N{\fs14}*Carry her, carry me*
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.80,0:40:04.69,cn,,0,0,0,,*轻启她的唇*\N{\fs14}*Moving silent her lips*
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.23,0:40:10.47,cn,,0,0,0,,*在那月光下*\N{\fs14}*By the moon's only light*
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.77,0:40:14.37,cn,,0,0,0,,*播散银色祝祷*\N{\fs14}*Sowing silver prayers*
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.54,0:40:18.61,cn,,0,0,0,,*在一片夜色中*\N{\fs14}*In the blanket of night.*
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.34,0:40:34.14,cn,,0,0,0,,快去拦住她\N{\fs14}Just go do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.16,0:40:36.40,cn,,0,0,0,,在这儿干坐着  你也不会更好过\N{\fs14}It ain't gonna get any easier, you sitting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.66,0:40:38.01,cn,,0,0,0,,我知道  可是...\N{\fs14}I-I know. - It just...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.02,0:40:39.51,cn,,0,0,0,,她要走了  快去\N{\fs14}You're gonna miss her. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.16,0:40:41.37,cn,,0,0,0,,快下车\N{\fs14}Get out of the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.07,0:40:44.01,cn,,0,0,0,,瑞秋\N{\fs14}Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.15,0:40:46.63,cn,,0,0,0,,听我说...\N{\fs14}Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.64,0:40:48.29,cn,,0,0,0,,杰森  很抱歉\N{\fs14}Jason, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.30,0:40:50.09,cn,,0,0,0,,我...  我该保持联络的\N{\fs14}I... I should've stayed in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.10,0:40:52.36,cn,,0,0,0,,我知道  我在父母家对你表现得怪怪的\N{\fs14}And I was weird to you at my parents', I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.37,0:40:53.28,cn,,0,0,0,,因为事情变得有点奇怪\N{\fs14}It's just, things have been strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.29,0:40:54.39,cn,,0,0,0,,我来不是谈这个的\N{\fs14}I'm not here to talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.52,0:40:55.67,cn,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14}Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.12,0:40:57.98,cn,,0,0,0,,你母亲提到一个卧底\N{\fs14}Your mom mentioned an undercover agent,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.00,0:41:00.13,cn,,0,0,0,,他出现在布莱恩的公寓  险些失血而死\N{\fs14}that he showed up at Brian's apartment, bleeding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.22,0:41:01.14,cn,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.28,0:41:03.87,cn,,0,0,0,,你能给我描述一下这个人吗\N{\fs14}Could you describe him for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.02,0:41:13.37,cn,,0,0,0,,今天这么安逸\N{\fs14}Banker's hours today?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.12,0:41:17.39,cn,,0,0,0,,是F地铁  有些晚点了\N{\fs14}"F" Train, there was some kind of delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.22,0:41:19.59,cn,,0,0,0,,我得跟布莱恩谈谈\N{\fs14}I need to talk to Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.60,0:41:20.59,cn,,0,0,0,,还没来\N{\fs14}Not in yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.84,0:41:22.54,cn,,0,0,0,,估计他跟你搭同一地铁\N{\fs14}I guess he took the same train.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.68,0:41:34.83,cn,,0,0,0,,我现在接不了电话\N{\fs14}I can't come to the phone right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.84,0:41:35.89,cn,,0,0,0,,如果有急事\N{\fs14}but if this is an emergency,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.90,0:41:37.81,cn,,0,0,0,,你可以随时联系丽贝卡·哈里斯\N{\fs14}you can try Rebecca Harris, any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.21,0:41:46.22,cn,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.37,0:41:57.43,cn,,0,0,0,,本想过来找你\N{\fs14}Thought about stopping by,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.44,0:41:59.37,cn,,0,0,0,,可我觉得你最近见我够多了\N{\fs14}but I figured you'd seen enough of me lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.94,0:42:01.48,cn,,0,0,0,,你应该知道一些事\N{\fs14}You should know a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.29,0:42:03.94,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}未接电话\N丽贝卡·哈里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.10,0:42:04.73,cn,,0,0,0,,很抱歉我说了那些话\N{\fs14}I'm sorry for the things I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.89,0:42:06.32,cn,,0,0,0,,我没理由那么说你\N{\fs14}You deserve better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.33,0:42:07.38,cn,,0,0,0,,无论发生什么事\N{\fs14}Whatever else happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.39,0:42:10.00,cn,,0,0,0,,你在我身上看到从没人发觉的潜能\N{\fs14}you saw potential in me that no one else ever did.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.32,0:42:13.17,cn,,0,0,0,,改变我人生的不仅仅是那种药  还有你\N{\fs14}It's not just the pill that changed my life, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.39,0:42:14.49,cn,,0,0,0,,所以  谢谢你\N{\fs14}So, thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.50,0:42:17.02,cn,,0,0,0,,事情暂时可能会有点疯狂\N{\fs14}Things may get a little crazy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.34,0:42:19.42,cn,,0,0,0,,我知道你对我的付出\N{\fs14}I know I haven't given back
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.43,0:42:20.90,cn,,0,0,0,,我还没有给予同样的回报\N{\fs14}as much as you've given me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.40,0:42:24.16,cn,,0,0,0,,也许我永远都做不到\N{\fs14}There's probably no way I ever could.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.18,0:42:27.80,cn,,0,0,0,,但从现在开始  我要试一试\N{\fs14}But starting now, I'm going to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.02,0:42:31.50,cn,,0,0,0,,为了尝试\N{\fs14}And in order to try,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.73,0:42:34.19,cn,,0,0,0,,我必须做一些事\N{\fs14}I've got to do a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.20,0:42:36.70,cn,,0,0,0,,所以你可能短期内联系不到我\N{\fs14}So you may not hear from me for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.28,0:42:37.27,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}私藏NZT药片  0粒
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.18,0:42:39.34,cn,,0,0,0,,我想我有办法把事情搞定\N{\fs14}I think I have a way to make some of this okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.28,0:42:38.06,cn,,0,0,0,,{\an8}私藏NZT药片  2粒
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.62,0:42:44.44,cn,,0,0,0,,如果一切顺利  过几天我就能见到你\N{\fs14}And if it all works out, I'll see you in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.45,0:42:46.20,cn,,0,0,0,,如果不顺利  那...\N{\fs14}And if it doesn't? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.43,0:42:49.55,cn,,0,0,0,,至少我们开心过  是吧\N{\fs14}we had some lulz, right?
